ble%20in%20hot%20weather%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoisture%20management%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20How%20quickly%20each%20shirt%20wicked%20sweat%2C%20dried%20after%20getting%20wet%2C%20and%20resisted%20feeling%20sticky%20or%20clammy%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Fabric%20feel%20against%20bare%20skin%2C%20stretch%2C%20freedom%20of%20movement%2C%20and%20whether%20seams%20or%20backpack%20straps%20caused%20irritation%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFit%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Overall%20cut%2C%20sleeve%20length%2C%20layering%20ability%2C%20and%20how%20the%20shirt%20performed%20during%20active%20movement%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EVersatility%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Whether%20the%20shirt%20worked%20for%20multiple%20activities%20like%20hiking%2C%20fishing%2C%20boating%2C%20travel%2C%20or%20everyday%20summer%20wear%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPackability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20How%20easily%20each%20shirt%20packed%20into%20a%20backpack%2C%20beach%20bag%2C%20or%20carry-on%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStyle%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Whether%20I'd%20actually%20want%20to%20wear%20it%20beyond%20the%20trail%20or%20water%2C%20along%20with%20color%20selection%20and%20overall%20design%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20no%20single%20sun%20shirt%20is%20perfect%20for%20every%20activity%2C%20I%20also%20considered%20where%20each%20one%20excelled%20most.%20Some%20are%20purpose-built%20for%20runners%2C%20others%20shine%20on%20the%20water%2C%20while%20a%20few%20are%20versatile%20enough%20to%20become%20everyday%20summer%20staples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222326bb7d-f675-4d2d-a76d-9a90852f9b83%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20the%20best%20sun%20shirts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%20of%20sun%20protection%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Any%20sun%20shirt%20worth%20its%20salt%20will%20have%20a%20UPF%20rating%2C%20measuring%20how%20effectively%20the%20fabric%20blocks%20UV%20rays.%20This%20is%20achieved%20either%20by%20how%20the%20fabric%20is%20constructed%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tighter%20weave%20will%20physically%20block%20UV%20rays%20from%20reaching%20your%20skin%20%E2%80%94%20or%20how%20the%20fabric%20is%20treated%2C%20namely%20with%20some%20kind%20of%20chemical.%20They%E2%80%99re%20both%20effective%2C%20but%20a%20treatment%20can%20gradually%20wash%20away%20over%20time%2C%20so%20for%20a%20sun%20shirt%20that%E2%80%99ll%20last%20season%20after%20season%2C%20look%20for%20shirts%20that%20highlight%20something%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Btight%20fabric%20construction%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20mention%20of%20the%20fabric%20being%20treated%20with%20a%20UV-absorbing%20compound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUPF%20rating%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdannyguo.md%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDanny%20Guo%2C%20MD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20double%20board-certified%20medical%2C%20surgical%2C%20and%20cosmetic%20dermatologist%20in%20Calgar%2C%20says%20the%20ideal%20UPF%20rating%20aligns%20with%20sunscreen%20best%20practices%20%E2%80%94%20UPF%2030%20should%20be%20the%20minimum%20a%20sun%20shirt%20offers%2C%20though%20UPF%2050%20is%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sun%20shirts%20are%20usually%20made%20from%20some%20kind%20of%20synthetic%20performance%20material%2C%20like%20polyester%20or%20nylon%2C%20since%20these%20fibers%20are%20easier%20to%20manipulate%20into%20a%20tighter%20weave%20to%20block%20UV%20rays.%20This%20is%20also%20the%20ideal%20material%20for%20workout%20or%20technical%20apparel%20since%20it%E2%80%99s%20great%20at%20wicking%20moisture%2C%20drying%20quickly%2C%20and%20letting%20air%20flow%20through%20on%20hot%20days.%20Other%20good%20news%3A%20Sun%20shirt%20fabrics%20are%20usually%20sensitive-skin%20friendly%20and%20well-tolerated%20by%20people%20with%20eczema%20or%20contact%20allergens%2C%20says%20Dr.%20Thosani.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%20and%20fit%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Because%20most%20people%20are%20wearing%20sun%20shirts%20during%20hot%20summer%20months%2C%20look%20for%20lightweight%20and%20breathable%20material%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20loose%20fitting%20design%2C%20Dr.%20Guo%20recommends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrand%20reliability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20reason%20it%E2%80%99s%20smart%20to%20buy%20a%20sun%20shirt%20from%20a%20trusted%20brand%3A%20%26quot%3BNot%20all%20sun%20shirts%20are%20built%20the%20same%20and%20the%20standards%20for%20regulating%20UPF%20clothing%20is%20not%20as%20rigid%20as%20sunscreen%20so%20it%20depends%20on%20the%20maker%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Guo%20points%20out.%20Stick%20with%20reputable%20outdoor%20clothing%20manufacturers%20like%20those%20on%20the%20list%20above.%20Bonus%20points%20if%20the%20shirt%20has%20the%20Seal%20of%20Recommendation%20from%20the%20Skin%20Cancer%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECoverage%20style%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENaturally%2C%20having%20a%20hood%2C%20high%20neck%2C%20and%20long%20sleeve%20are%20the%20most%20ideal%20for%20the%20ultimate%20sun%20protection.%20But%20be%20realistic%20about%20what%20you%20need%3A%20Some%20people%20may%20prefer%20a%20loose%20crew%20neck%20or%20collared%20shirt%20combined%20with%20a%20UPF%20sun%20hat%20to%20cover%20the%20neck%2C%20or%20a%20short%20sleeve%20UPF%20shirt%20with%20regular%20application%20of%20sunscreen%20down%20the%20exposed%20arms%20and%20neck.%20A%20combination%20approach%20is%20always%20reasonable%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20you%E2%80%99re%20protecting%20all%20your%20exposed%20skin%2C%20Dr.%20Thosani%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20a%20shirt%20looks%20damaged%20or%20faded%2C%20consider%20getting%20a%20new%20one%20to%20ensure%20the%20UPF%20value%20is%20still%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b005eb6e-b4b9-4622-9784-9ac9bd377eae%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Meet%20the%20expert%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeet%20the%20expert%20behind%20this%20guide%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Split%20image%20shows%20one%20person%20rowing%20on%20a%20river%20and%20another%20standing%20on%20a%20wooded%20trail%20with%20a%20dog.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d2a015dc133dbf310dace%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Frachael-schultz%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERachael%20Schultz%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20health%2C%20fitness%2C%20and%20outdoor%20journalist%20with%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20of%20experience%20testing%20technical%20apparel%20and%20gear%2C%20largely%20from%20her%20home%20base%20in%20the%20Colorado%20mountains.%20She%20has%20reviewed%20hundreds%20of%20products%20across%20categories%20including%20hiking%20boots%2C%20rain%20jackets%2C%20running%20gear%2C%20recovery%20footwear%2C%20camping%20equipment%2C%20and%20outdoor%20clothing%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20separating%20real-world%20performance%20and%20frustrations%20from%20hyped%20marketing%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20avid%20whitewater%20rafter%2C%20hiker%2C%20and%20runner%20around%20her%20home%20in%20sunny%20Colorado%2C%20Schultz%20has%20years%20of%20testing%20sun-protective%20clothing%20and%20delineating%20a%20good%20sun%20shirt%20from%20a%20mediocre%20option.%20For%20this%20guide%2C%20Schultz%20tested%2042%20sun%20shirts%20from%20leading%20outdoor%20and%20athletic%20brands%2C%20wearing%20them%20throughout%20the%20spring%20and%20summer%20while%20hiking%2C%20running%2C%20boating%2C%20and%20spending%20everyday%20life%20outdoors%20in%20the%20Colorado%20mountains.%20She%20also%20incorporated%20additional%20wear%20testing%20from%20her%20husband%20who%20works%20part-time%20as%20a%20landscaper%20and%20spends%20much%20of%20his%20free%20time%20on%20the%20river%20or%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a96ddbcd-cc1b-4493-9758-1f1ca73768dd%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFAQs%20on%20sun%20shirts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20I%20need%20a%20sun%20shirt%20if%20I%20already%20put%20on%20sunscreen%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20UPF%20clothing%20plays%20the%20same%20role%20as%20sunscreen%2C%20so%20it%20depends%20where%20you've%20applied%20the%20SPF%20lotion.%20At%20the%20beach%20or%20pool%2C%20most%20of%20our%20skin%20is%20exposed%20and%2C%20ideally%2C%20already%20lathered%20with%20SPF%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20wear%20a%20sun%20shirt%20unless%20you%20want%20an%20added%20layer%20of%20protection%2C%20assuming%20you%20are%20reapplying%20sunscreen%20regularly%20and%20properly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20everyday%20life%20or%20during%20outdoor%20activities%2C%20most%20people%20only%20apply%20sunscreen%20on%20sun-exposed%20areas%20like%20the%20face%2C%20neck%2C%20hands%2C%20and%20arms%2C%20points%20out%20Dr.%20Guo.%20%26quot%3BNormal%20T-shirts%20have%20a%20UPF%20value%20of%20around%205%20to%207%20and%20that%20drops%20to%203%20when%20the%20shirt%20gets%20wet%20from%20sweating%2C%20for%20example%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20This%20can%20create%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinverse%20burn%E2%80%9D%20where%20you%20have%20more%20sun%20damage%20under%20their%20clothes%20than%20where%20they%20are%20exposed%2C%20he%20adds.%20Wearing%20UPF%20clothing%20will%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20this%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20sun%20shirts%20are%20sometimes%20even%20more%20reliable%20than%20sunscreen%20due%20to%20sunscreen%20wearing%20off%20over%20time%2C%20skin%20getting%20wet%2C%20and%20inconsistent%20applications%2C%20Dr.%20Guo%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20sun%20shirts%20really%20shield%20you%20from%20skin%20damage%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20they%20absolutely%20work%20at%20protecting%20your%20skin%2C%20both%20experts%20agree.%20UPF%20fabrics%20have%20a%20tighter%20weave%20density%20which%20allows%20less%20light%20to%20penetrate%20through%2C%20and%20the%20fabric%20and%20fibers%20that%20are%20used%20to%20make%20it%20naturally%20block%20UV%20better%2C%20Dr.%20Thosani%20explains.%20Many%20UPF%20shirts%20have%20chemical%20UV%20absorbers%20that%20are%20bonded%20into%20the%20fabric%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20all%20sun%20shirts%20are%20built%20the%20same%2C%20Dr.%20Guo%20points%20out%2C%20and%20the%20standards%20for%20regulating%20UPF%20clothing%20are%20not%20as%20rigid%20as%20sunscreen%20so%20it%20depends%20on%20the%20manufacturer.%20Also%2C%20UPF%20clothing%20can%20also%20lose%20efficacy%20with%20wear%20and%20tear%20or%20washing%20over%20time%2C%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhen%20should%20I%20wear%20a%20sun%20shirt%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESunshirts%20are%20great%20any%20time%20you're%20going%20outside%20for%20a%20short%20stint%20and%20don't%20want%20to%20fully%20lather%20your%20body%20in%20SPF%2C%20like%20walking%20the%20dog%20or%20chatting%20with%20your%20neighbor%20(although%20you%20should%20put%20sunscreen%20on%20any%20exposed%20skin%20not%20covered%20by%20the%20shirt).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20smart%20to%20wear%20a%20sunshirt%20any%20time%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20outside%20for%20a%20long%20period%20and%20aren't%20likely%20to%20reapply%20SPF%20cream%2C%20like%20a%20game%20of%20golf%20or%20taking%20a%20nap%20by%20the%20pool%2C%20our%20experts%20adds.%20Also%2C%20people%20who%20sunburn%20easily%20or%20often%20forget%20to%20reapply%20sunscreen%20should%20consider%20wearing%20UPF%20clothing%20most%20any%20time%20they're%20outside%2C%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhen%20does%20a%20sun%20shirt%20stop%20being%20effective%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EUPF%20fabrics%20are%20generally%20well%20made%2C%20long%20lasting%2C%20breathable%2C%20comfortable%2C%20and%20reusable%2C%20but%20they%20%26quot%3Bexpire%26quot%3B%20when%20they%E2%80%99ve%20become%20worn%2C%20stretched%2C%20or%20have%20holes%2C%20Dr.%20Thosani%20says.%20The%20UPF%20protection%20comes%20from%20a%20garment%E2%80%99s%20tight%20weave%20and%2C%20potentially%2C%20any%20additional%20UV-absorbing%20treatment%20that%E2%80%99s%20been%20added%20to%20it.%20That%20means%20when%20wear-and-tear%20compromises%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20fibers%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20replace%20your%20sun%20shirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-sun-shirts%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783857601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5163409d0a41df475c91e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-sun-shirts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20tested%2042%20sun%20shirts%20with%20the%20help%20of%20my%20landscaper%20husband%20to%20find%20lightweight%2C%20UPF-rated%20designs%20that%20wick%20sweat%20and%20stay%20cool%20in%20the%20summer%20heat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rschultz%40insider.com%20(Rachael%20Schultz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20doctor%20continues%20to%20rock%20India%20without%20missing%20a%20beat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783857434000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132345205%2Cimgsize-162516.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fhow-a-doctor-continues-to-rock-india-without-missing-a-beat%2Farticleshow%2F132345195.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Palash%20Sen%2C%20frontman%20of%20Delhi-based%20band%2C%20Euphoria%2C%20recounts%20his%20capital%20life%20and%20explains%20why%20the%20music%20changed%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22AVIJIT%20GHOSH%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dhanush%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Om%E2%80%99%20begins%20final%20Malaysia%20schedule%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%