%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e8e44d3b3e45765196a20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221708%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20vowed%20to%20care%20for%20her%20parents%20as%20they%20aged.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lindsay%20Karp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20always%20envisioned%20caring%20for%20my%20parents%20as%20they%20aged.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20I've%20lived%20with%20multiple%20sclerosis%20for%20two%20decades%2C%20which%20makes%20things%20more%20difficult.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20mom%20recently%20had%20surgery%2C%20which%20threw%20this%20reality%20into%20sharp%20relief.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20try%20to%20meet%20you%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20told%20my%20mother%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20one%20evening%20before%20bed.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20feeling%20great%2C%20but%20I'll%20do%20my%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20confirmed%20before%20hanging%20up%20the%20phone.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20my%2071-year-old%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuprooted-life-financial-costs-caregiving-sick-mother-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emother%20had%20surgery%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20lift%20her%20bladder.%20My%2074-year-old%20father%20is%20a%20stage%204%20tongue%20cancer%20survivor%20now%20dealing%20with%20the%20overwhelming%20downstream%20effects%20of%20radiation%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20live%20with%20multiple%20sclerosis%20(MS)%20%E2%80%94%20so%20usually%20my%20otherwise%20healthy%20mother%20plays%20the%20caregiver%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20present%20at%20most%20of%20my%20appointments%20during%20the%2013%20years%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmisdiagnosed-for-13-years-neurologist-found-i-have-ms-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esearched%20for%20a%20diagnosis%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20early%20adulthood.%20She%20attends%20every%20medical%20visit%20with%20my%20father%20and%20often%20takes%20me%20for%20my%20immunosuppressive%20infusion.%20She%20was%20beside%20me%20for%20the%20birth%20of%20my%20older%20son%20in%202011%20and%20later%20cared%20for%20him%20when%20my%20younger%20son%20was%20born%20in%202014.%20Lying%20in%20the%20hospital%20bed%20that%20Monday%20morning%2C%20she%20threw%20our%20normal%20family%20narrative%20off%20kilter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e2226bae-3c48-42c6-ad83-aeae43b1c7da%5C%22%3EI'd%20never%20seen%20my%20mom%20that%20vulnerable%20before%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20walked%20into%20her%20hospital%20room%20just%20as%20she%20arrived%20post-recovery%2C%20the%20anesthesia%20still%20swirling%20through%20her%20system.%20%26quot%3BCan%20you%20fill%20this%20out%20for%20me%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked%2C%20handing%20me%20the%20cafeteria%20menu%20for%20her%20overnight%20stay.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20read%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued%2C%20her%20words%20ever%20so%20slightly%20slurred.%20In%20that%20moment%2C%20it%20occurred%20to%20me%20that%20I'd%20never%20seen%20her%20like%20this%3A%20vulnerable%20and%20dependent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPasta%20alfredo%20with%20chicken%20or%20mac%20and%20cheese%20for%20dinner%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20asked%2C%20chuckling%2C%20knowing%20a%20discussion%20of%20the%20absurdity%20of%20a%20hospital%20offering%20only%20pasta%20options%20would%20ensue.%20%26quot%3BI'll%20write-in%20%3Cem%3Echicken%20breast%20with%20vegetables%20and%20rice%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20suggested%2C%20handing%20her%20the%20cranberry%20juice%20that%20had%20been%20left%20just%20beyond%20her%20reach.%20She%20asked%20me%20to%20plug%20in%20her%20cellphone%20charger%20before%20reading%20the%20remaining%20menu%20options.%20As%20I%20moved%20around%20the%20room%20with%20purpose%2C%20my%20legs%20jittered%2C%20and%20my%20hands%20shook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnot-fun-mom-multiple-sclerosis-husband-steps-in-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20with%20MS%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20two%20decades%2C%20and%20it%20always%20flares%20at%20the%20worst%20possible%20times%3B%20stress%20makes%20it%20worse.%20As%20I%20struggled%20to%20stand%2C%20I%20realized%20this%20disease%20that%20had%20affected%20my%20personal%20functioning%20and%20my%20ability%20to%20parent%20for%20decades%20was%20now%20impeding%20my%20capacity%20to%20care%20for%20my%20mother%2C%20something%20I'd%20always%20imagined%20I'd%20do%20without%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221647%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20author%20and%20her%20parents%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e8e9fd3b3e45765196a27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221235%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20lives%20with%20MS%2C%20which%20may%20make%20being%20her%20parents'%20caregiver%20more%20difficult.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lindsay%20Karp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22641d4ff6-2c3b-449e-a15a-1513a3b85060%5C%22%3EI've%20always%20pictured%20myself%20caring%20for%20my%20parents%20as%20they%20get%20older%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20younger%2C%20my%20paternal%20grandfather%20stayed%20at%20our%20home%20while%20recovering%20from%20surgery.%20I'd%20arrive%20home%20from%20school%20to%20find%20him%20resting%20in%20his%20favorite%20recliner.%20My%20maternal%20great-grandmother%20came%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flived-with-grandmother-during-college-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elive%20with%20my%20grandmom%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20her%20final%20months.%20I%20remember%20watching%20my%20grandmother%20bring%20a%20turkey%20and%20cheese%20sandwich%20to%20her%20bedside%2C%20tending%20to%20her%20just%20as%20I%20imagine%20my%20great-grandmother%20had%20done%20for%20my%20grandmom%20when%20she%20was%20sick%20as%20a%20child.%20I%20still%20recall%20that%20scene%20vividly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20tables%20have%20turned%2C%20and%20my%20mother%20takes%20my%2094-year-old%20grandmother%20to%20run%20errands%20weekly%20and%20to%20doctor's%20visits%20as%20they%20arise.%20She's%20been%20back%20and%20forth%20to%20the%20hospital%20with%20her%20as%20she%20struggles%20with%20lymphedema%20and%20infections%20in%20her%20legs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20one%20day%20I%2C%20too%2C%20will%20find%20myself%20in%20the%20caregiver%20role.%20Just%20as%20I%20stayed%20home%20with%20my%20babies%2C%20not%20wanting%20someone%20else%20to%20raise%20them%2C%20I've%20always%20aspired%20to%20personally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuilt-house-dad-dementia-caregiving-costs-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecare%20for%20my%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20the%20time%20came%2C%20especially%20after%20my%20grandfather%2C%20who%20was%20living%20with%20Alzheimer's%2C%20was%20involved%20in%20an%20incident%20at%20his%20nursing%20home%20that%20still%20haunts%20me%20and%20my%20family%2010%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20father%20is%20living%20with%20severe%20dysphagia%20(i.e.%2C%20swallowing%20disability)%2C%20a%20voice%20disorder%2C%20blood%20pressure%20lability%2C%20and%20a%20smattering%20of%20other%20issues%20secondary%20to%20radiation%20to%20the%20head%20and%20neck%20two%20decades%20ago.%20He%20now%20uses%20a%20feeding%20tube%2C%20and%20his%20voice%20is%20permanently%20hoarse%20and%20extremely%20difficult%20to%20understand.%20%26quot%3BWill%20you%20be%20my%20voice%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20texted%20me%20the%20day%20before%20my%20parents'%2050%3Csup%3Eth%3C%2Fsup%3E%20anniversary%20celebration%20last%20November.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20like%20you%20to%20read%20this%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20of%20a%20toast%20he'd%20written%20for%20my%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20following%20my%20mother's%20surgery%2C%20I%20checked%20him%20into%20the%20visitor's%20center%20at%20the%20hospital%20where%20he'd%20struggled%20to%20be%20understood%20the%20day%20before.%20Watching%20him%20flounder%20rattles%20me%2C%20but%20knowing%20I%20can%20alleviate%20some%20of%20his%20struggle%20is%20reassuring.%20I%20was%20glad%20I%20was%20there%20beside%20him%20to%20walk%20the%20halls%20to%20her%20room%20that%20morning%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flifestyle-changes-to-lower-blood-pressure-early-family-history-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblood%20pressure%20instability%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20left%20him%20lightheaded%20and%20in%20need%20of%20a%20seat%20often.%20My%20strong%20and%20capable%20father%2C%20who%20once%20fixed%20broken%20knickknacks%2C%20remedied%20car%20troubles%2C%20and%20built%20a%20kitchen%20closet%20from%20scratch%2C%20now%20relies%20on%20me%20in%20ways%20I%20never%20imagined%20he%20would.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2276d7fb50-2726-404d-a71e-9be0dcca0b22%5C%22%3EMy%20diagnosis%20has%20made%20my%20vision%20for%20the%20future%20feel%20more%20difficult%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESlowly%2C%20the%20time%20of%20need%20I've%20envisioned%20since%20childhood%20is%20creeping%20toward%20me%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20the%20strong%20adult%20of%20my%20youthful%20imagination.%20I'm%20realizing%20I%20can't%20be%20the%20boundless%20caregiver%20I%20always%20thought%20I'd%20be.%20I%20can't%20drive%20endless%20miles%20with%20a%20foot%20that%20often%20struggles%20to%20hold%20the%20pedal.%20I%20can't%20walk%20the%20perimeter%20of%20a%20hospital%20and%20back%20again%20with%20legs%20that%20weaken%20from%20simply%20existing.%20And%20last-minute%20visits%20to%20the%20store%20aren't%20as%20simple%20for%20someone%20living%20with%20chronic%20weakness%20and%20fatigue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falmost-lost-my-father-live-in-the-moment-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efather's%20medical%20battles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20continues%20to%20work%20full%20time%20as%20a%20civil%20engineer%20and%20president%20of%20his%20firm%20because%20he%20maintains%20the%20vivacious%20spirit%20I've%20never%20known%20him%20without.%20My%20mother%20has%20fully%20recovered%20from%20her%20procedure%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20caregiver%20I've%20always%20known%20her%20to%20be.%20They%20don't%20need%20me%20just%20yet%2C%20but%20watching%20her%20in%20the%20hospital%20and%20moving%20slowly%20against%20pain%20in%20the%20following%20weeks%20at%20home%20gave%20me%20a%20glimpse%20of%20how%20they%20may%20need%20me%20one%20day%20soon%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20reality%20of%20my%20own%20limitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%2C%20I%20promised%20myself%20I'd%20care%20for%20them%20just%20as%20they%20always%20did%20for%20me.%20My%20caregiving%20won't%20be%20perfect%2C%20but%20I'm%20going%20to%20give%20them%20everything%20my%20body%20will%20allow%3B%20my%20voice%2C%20a%20turkey%20and%20cheese%20sandwich%2C%20and%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaregiving-for-aging-parents-reality-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783856461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e8e44d3b3e45765196a20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaregiving-for-aging-parents-reality-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20promised%20myself%20I'd%20care%20for%20my%20parents%20as%20they%20got%20older.%20However%2C%20I'm%20living%20with%20MS%2C%20and%20being%20a%20caregiver%20may%20be%20difficult.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lindsay%20Karp)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NY%20Mayor%20Zohran%20Mamdani%20revives%20%E2%80%98Click-To-Cancel%E2%80%99%20rule%20opposed%20by%20Comcast%2C%20Disney%20and%20others%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783856366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132345040%2Cimgsize-54963.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fnew-york-mayor-zohran-mayor-b