d%20possessed%20a%20valid%20license.%20The%20building%20owner%20declined%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%2C%20so%20no%20FIR%20was%20registered.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A100%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Badly%20burned%20British%20couple%20rescued%20from%20ravine%20during%20Spain%20wildfires%2C%20reports%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783855389000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Face%2Fbranded_news%2F1200%2Fcpsprodpb%2F8883%2Flive%2F9b0fc300-7dda-11f1-91f9-abeb669686c2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx2x7441762o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20unnamed%20pair%20were%20found%20semi-conscious%20with%2040%25%20burns%20after%20being%20trapped%20by%20the%20blazes%20raging%20through%20Almeria%20province%2C%20according%20to%20local%20media%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx2x7441762o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20out%20of%20Punjab%20poll%20race%2C%20says%20BJP%20leader%20Fatehjung%20Singh%20Bajwa%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783855159000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132344667%2Cimgsize-83566.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fits-own-members-tear-each-other-apart-congress-out-of-punjab-poll-race-says-bjps-bajwa%2Farticleshow%2F132344533.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Punjab%20BJP%20leader%20stated%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20not%20in%20the%20race%20for%202027.%20He%20believes%20the%20party%20will%20struggle%20to%20retain%20its%20existing%20eighteen%20seats.%20Congress%20leaders%20themselves%20allege%20compromises%20with%20the%20current%20state%20government.%20Party%20officials%20deny%20any%20internal%20factionalism%20and%20express%20unity%20for%20upcoming%20polls.%20Unity%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20party%2C%20but%20compromised%20leaders%20should%20be%20avoided.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20love%20taking%20staycations%20with%20my%20kids.%20I%20always%20book%20a%20hotel%20with%20a%20pool%2C%20and%20typical%20rules%20go%20out%20the%20window.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20with%20her%20son.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4fc052d3a449ec3445fbd8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20doesn't%20wait%20for%20her%20whole%20family%20to%20be%20free%20to%20take%20staycations%20with%20her%20kids.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jamie%20Davis%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20take%20my%20kids%20on%20staycations%20a%20couple%20of%20times%20a%20year%20as%20a%20surprise.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20book%20hotels%20within%20two%20hours%20of%20home%2C%20and%20we%20only%20stay%20one%20or%20two%20nights.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20all%20have%20fun%2C%20and%20I%20often%20return%20home%20more%20refreshed%20than%20when%20we%20go%20on%20longer%20vacations.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20fortunate%20to%20be%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsimple-tips-smoother-trips-travel-kids-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etravel%20with%20my%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20often.%20However%2C%20sometimes%20the%20travel%20bug%20bites%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20time%2C%20energy%2C%20or%20budget%20for%20a%20true%20vacation.%20When%20that%20happens%2C%20I%20plan%20a%20staycation%20close%20to%20our%20home%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20Although%20staycations%20admittedly%20don't%20have%20the%20same%20thrill%20as%20a%20full-fledged%20international%20trip%2C%20they%20can%20still%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiscovering%20new%20things%20together%2C%20away%20from%20the%20demands%20and%20routine%20of%20daily%20life%2C%20is%20how%20my%20family%20and%20I%20have%20made%20some%20of%20our%20best%20memories.%20I%20discovered%20that%20booking%20a%20hotel%20a%20few%20blocks%20away%20from%20home%20can%20be%20almost%20as%20memorable%20as%20a%20trip%20halfway%20around%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20if%20I%20plan%20correctly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20downside%20of%20staycations%20is%20that%20my%20children%20now%20want%20to%20take%20them%20all%20the%20time.%20Though%20it's%20not%20feasible%20to%20take%20one%20every%20month%2C%20I%20usually%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsummer-travel-america-stay-home-staycation-high-oil-prices-tsa-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplan%20a%20staycation%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20couple%20of%20times%20a%20year%20as%20a%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fd540e95-9b19-4a2f-8556-f3d599397c30%5C%22%3EI%20keep%20the%20logistics%20simple%20and%20switch%20to%20vacation%20mode%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20hard-and-fast%20rules%20for%20staycations%2C%20but%20I%20try%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstay-at-hotel-by-myself-mental-health-relationship-benefits-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estick%20to%20hotels%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20two%20hours%20of%20home.%20We%20usually%20go%20away%20for%20one%20or%20two%20nights%2C%20although%20I%20often%20wish%20I%20had%20planned%20to%20stay%20longer.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20plan%20in%20advance%2C%20and%20other%20times%20I%20scroll%20to%20see%20if%20I%20can%20find%20a%20good%20last-minute%20deal%20if%20we%20happen%20to%20have%20a%20rare%20weekend%20without%20any%20obligations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20the%20most%20of%20our%20staycations%2C%20I%20always%20ask%20for%20early%20check-in%20and%20late%20check-out.%20Even%20if%20that's%20not%20possible%2C%20the%20hotel%20will%20usually%20store%20my%20luggage%20and%20give%20us%20access%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freformer-pilates-new-luxury-hotel-amenity-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehotel%20amenities%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20the%20pool%20for%20the%20entire%20day%20we%20check%20in%20or%20out%2C%20which%20can%20make%20our%20time%20away%20feel%20much%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20don't%20wait%20for%20a%20time%20that%20works%20for%20my%20entire%20family.%20While%20I%20love%20having%20my%20family%20of%20six%20together%2C%20that's%20not%20always%20possible%20because%20of%20school%2C%20work%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyouth-sports-expensive-competitive-huge-commitment-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esports%20schedules%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20times%2C%20I%20may%20bring%20one%20or%20two%20of%20my%20four%20kids%20on%20a%20staycation%2C%20because%20if%20I%20waited%20for%20everyone's%20schedules%20to%20align%2C%20I%20might%20find%20myself%20waiting%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20staycations%2C%20I%20switch%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fslowcation-travel-trend-tourists-booking-longer-trips-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evacation%20mode%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20if%20we%20are%20within%20a%20few%20minutes%20of%20home.%20I%20allow%20my%20kids%20to%20order%20soda%20and%20dessert%2C%20rare%20treats%20during%20our%20everyday%20lives.%20We%20often%20stay%20up%20late%2C%20playing%20UNO%20or%20Clue%2C%20games%20my%20kids%20love%2C%20but%20we%20somehow%20can't%20manage%20to%20fit%20in%20during%20the%20business%20of%20everyday%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221664%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20author's%20son%20in%20a%20pool%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4fc128b3a8c16f7e8ece95%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221248%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20always%20books%20a%20hotel%20with%20a%20pool.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jamie%20Davis%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227766990e-75b0-4d5c-97ac-a2ac43ceeb03%5C%22%3EI%20always%20pick%20a%20hotel%20that%20has%20a%20pool%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family's%20first%20staycation%20started%20with%20my%20son's%20request%20to%20go%20swimming%20on%20his%20birthday.%20Swimming%20was%20the%20only%20present%20he%20asked%20for%2C%20but%20since%20he%20was%20born%20in%20the%20depths%20of%20winter%2C%20it%20wasn't%20easy%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%20My%20solution%20was%20to%20book%20a%20nearby%20hotel%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findoor-pool-in-house-renovation-diy-cost-regret-tennessee-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindoor%20pool%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20entire%20family%20had%20so%20much%20fun%20that%20now%2C%20I%20will%20only%20book%20hotels%20with%20pools%20when%20we%20take%20a%20staycation.%20However%2C%20after%20we%20once%20checked%20into%20a%20hotel%20and%20discovered%20the%20pool%20was%20closed%20for%20renovations%2C%20I%20now%20call%20to%20verify%20the%20pool%20will%20be%20open%20before%20booking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223ccd1e5-c8f4-4e8d-978d-b7ccb1ec9cac%5C%22%3EI%20book%20staycations%20at%20hotels%20with%20on-site%20activities%20or%20easy%20access%20to%20activities%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20staycations%20are%20short%2C%20time%20is%20at%20a%20premium.%20Some%20of%20my%20family's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-plan-the-perfect-staycation-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efavorite%20staycations%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20at%20nearby%20resorts%20with%20on-site%20activities.%20Nearby%20Gaylord%20National%20Resort%20and%20Convention%20Center%20often%20hosts%20events%2C%20so%20we%20don't%20have%20to%20leave%20the%20premises%20at%20all.%20Another%20favorite%20staycation%20destination%2C%20Great%20Wolf%20Lodge%2C%20has%20a%20huge%20waterpark%20and%20nightly%20dance%20parties%20that%20my%20kids%20love%20almost%20as%20much%20as%20the%20Caribbean%20resorts%20we%20have%20visited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20stay%20somewhere%20without%20a%20ton%20of%20on-site%20activities%2C%20I%20try%20to%20at%20least%20book%20near%20places%20we%20want%20to%20go%20during%20our%20staycation.%20I%20also%20include%20at%20least%20one%20special%20activity%20that%20my%20kids%20have%20been%20asking%20to%20do.%20One%20particularly%20memorable%20staycation%20was%20at%20the%20historic%20Watergate%2C%20not%20far%20from%20Georgetown's%20waterfront%20and%20museums%20on%20the%20National%20Mall%2C%20which%20kept%20us%20busy.%20A%20couple%20of%20times%2C%20ice%20skating%20was%20the%20highlight%20of%20our%20staycation.%20Once%2C%20it%20was%20a%20kid-friendly%20interactive%20exhibit%20at%20a%20local%20museum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221664%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20author's%20family%20at%20ICE!%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4fc0c4b3a8c16f7e8ece90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221248%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20family%20have%20stayed%20at%20Gaylord%20National%20Resort%20and%20Convention%20Center%2C%20which%20hosts%20ICE!%20each%20winter.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jamie%20Davis%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fd2c251d-23e4-48ef-b940-3cc97f32e9ae%5C%22%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20staycations%20are%20even%20better%20than%20vacations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20staycations%20actually%20have%20significant%20benefits%20over%20faraway%20vacations%2C%20beyond%20cost%20and%20shorter%20duration.%20They%20are%20easier%20to%20plan%20because%20I%20am%20already%20familiar%20with%20the%20area%2C%20I%20know%20how%20to%20get%20around%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20need%20to%20research%20things%20to%20do%20or%20where%20to%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20after%20I%20return%20from%20a%20staycation%2C%20I%20truly%20feel%20relaxed%20and%20refreshed%20even%20if%20I%20have%20only%20been%20away%20for%20a%20night%20or%20two.%20When%20I%20take%20trips%20that%20last%20a%20week%20or%20more%2C%20I%20often%20feel%20depleted%20from%20constantly%20being%20on%20the%20go%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20nice%20change.%20And%20unlike%20longer%20vacations%20farther%20from%20home%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20mountain%20of%20laundry%20to%20do%20and%20piles%20of%20mail%20to%20sort%20through%20once%20the%20staycation%20is%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20enjoy%20taking%20vacations%20whenever%20I%20can%2C%20but%20I%20also%20treasure%20the%20time%20my%20family%20spends%20together%20during%20staycations%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstaycations-with-kids-hotel-pool-no-rules-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783855021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4fc052d3a449ec3445fbd8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstaycations-with-kids-hotel-pool-no-rules-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20take%20staycations%20with%20my%20kids%20a%20few%20times%20a%20year.%20I%20make%20sure%20our%20hotel%20has%20a%20pool%20and%20go%20on%20'vacation%20mode%2C'%20even%20if%20we're%20just%20a%20few%20minutes%20away.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jamie%20Davis%20Smith)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20Woman%2C%20Son%20Arrested%20In%20Karnataka%20For%20Hiding%20Nationality%20In%20Documents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22A%20criminal%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20the%20two%20under%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS)%2C%20the%20Foreigners%20Act%2C%20and%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783854988000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-07%2F8usds6e8_bengaluru-police_625x300_12_July_26.jpeg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3D