A%20Why%20mental%20illnesses%20remain%20so%20misunderstood%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783854547000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132344418%2Cimgsize-94436.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwhen-myths-become-diagnoses-why-mental-illnesses-remain-so-misunderstood%2Farticleshow%2F132344298.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20increasing%20awareness%20of%20mental%20health%2C%20public%20comprehension%20still%20lags%20behind%20scientific%20advancements.%20Misunderstandings%20surrounding%20schizophrenia%2C%20dissociative%20identity%20disorder%2C%20and%20bipolar%20disorder%20lead%20to%20widespread%20stigma.%20The%20media%20often%20dramatizes%20these%20issues%2C%20portraying%20affected%20individuals%20as%20violent%20or%20erratic.%20To%20combat%20this%2C%20we%20need%20to%20prioritize%20education%20and%20foster%20empathy%2C%20while%20robust%20support%20systems%20must%20aid%20patients%20and%20caregivers%20in%20their%20journey%20toward%20recovery%20and%20respect.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TRISHA%20MAHAJAN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20was%20laid%20off%20at%2056%20and%20took%20a%2060%25%20pay%20cut%20to%20land%20my%20next%20role%20%E2%80%94%20the%20biggest%20thing%20I%20feel%20is%20anger%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224096%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Christina%20Jones%20headshot%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a50f6aed9d92978fe6a549d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChristina%20Jones%20says%20many%20older%20job-seekers%20want%20an%20opportunity%20to%20continue%20doing%20what%20they%20love.%3Cp%3EChristina%20Jones%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChristina%20Jones%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20United%20healthcare%20in%202025%20after%2015%20years%20at%20the%20company%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJones%20struggled%20to%20find%20a%20job%20until%20she%20accepted%20a%20role%20outside%20of%20her%20scope%20with%20a%2060%25%20pay%20cut.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20is%20budgeting%20and%20downsizing%20while%20continuing%20to%20search%20for%20opportunities%20in%20her%20desired%20field.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Christina%20Jones%2C%20a%2057-year-old%20in%20Philadelphia.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20didn't%20expect%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-meta-employee-shares-what-she-wishes-she-knew-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elaid%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20my%20business%20analyst%20role%20at%20United%20Healthcare%20last%20year%2C%20after%2015%20years%20at%20the%20company%2C%20I%20wasn't%20shocked.%20Layoffs%20are%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20beast%20in%20the%20corporate%20world.%20What%20shocked%20me%20more%20was%20how%20long%20it%20took%20me%20to%20find%20another%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20through%20interview%20after%20interview%20throughout%20the%20next%20year%2C%20and%20nothing%20came%20of%20it.%20I%20truly%20believe%20it%20was%20because%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F50-unemployed-worried-hiring-managers-see-desperation-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eapplying%20at%2056%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20wasn't%20until%20I%20took%20a%20job%20outside%20my%20desired%20scope%20and%20with%20a%2060%25%20pay%20cut%20that%20I%20got%20rehired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20had%20to%20make%20major%20lifestyle%20changes%2C%20and%20we're%20even%20selling%20our%20house.%20I'm%20scared%20about%20what%20the%20future%20will%20hold%2C%20but%20the%20biggest%20thing%20I%20feel%20is%20anger.%20I%20won't%20give%20up%20on%20finding%20another%20job%20in%20healthcare%20IT.%20It's%20my%20passion%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20continue%20doing%20what%20I%20enjoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b8fb0a6-0073-4ef8-8b86-e49f2852398c%5C%22%3EI%20took%20a%20pay%20cut%2C%20but%20I'm%20still%20fighting%20to%20get%20back%20into%20the%20role%20I%20want%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20prove%20that%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-interviews-at-50-ghosted-motivation-strategy-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eage%20is%20working%20against%20me%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20job%20hunt.%20It's%20a%20feeling.%20It%20seems%20like%20whenever%20a%20potential%20employer%20finds%20out%20my%20birthday%2C%20they%20don't%20call%20me%20back%2C%20or%20the%20rejection%20email%20comes%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%20of%202025%2C%20my%20mom%20ended%20up%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20and%20I%20was%20talking%20to%20the%20nurses%20there%20about%20my%20job%20experience%20hunting.%20They%20encouraged%20me%20to%20apply%20to%20work%20there%2C%20and%20although%20I%20wanted%20to%20stay%20in%20IT%2C%20I%20applied%20anyway%20and%20got%20the%20job%20as%20a%20patient%20safety%20associate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20it%20was%20at%20a%20very%20reduced%20rate%20from%20my%20last%20job%2C%20but%20I%20took%20it%20anyway.%20I'm%20still%20employed%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20but%20I%20haven't%20stopped%20trying%20to%20get%20back%20into%20IT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22808bb406-fbfe-442e-909b-95368ee28348%5C%22%3EWe've%20had%20to%20make%20major%20lifestyle%20changes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-job-at-53-using-multi-month-exit-plan-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecareer%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20are%20having%20to%20move%20out%20of%20our%20home.%20There%20have%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20moments%20of%20doubt%20and%20worry%20about%20how%20we're%20going%20to%20get%20through%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20use%20any%20of%20the%20amenities%20that%20we%20used%20to.%20We%20used%20to%20go%20out%20to%20eat%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20now%20we're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcooked-meals-at-home-month-how-it-went-tips-dishes-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecooking%20at%20home%20more%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20upside%20is%20that%20I've%20learned%20to%20cook.%20We%20also%20canceled%20our%20annual%20tickets%20to%20Longwood%20Gardens%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20really%20have%20the%20funds%20to%20do%20fun%20things.%20Fortunately%2C%20our%20youngest%20child%20just%20turned%2018%2C%20so%20we%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20financially%20support%20them%20like%20we%20used%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254e65e83-8b36-44a8-819d-ffbc8f0e4786%5C%22%3EThe%20biggest%20thing%20I%20feel%20is%20anger%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20come%20across%20jobs%20that%20are%20perfect%20for%20me%20and%20fit%20exactly%20what%20I've%20done%20throughout%20my%20career%2C%20only%20to%20get%20rejected%20before%20a%20phone%20interview%2C%20is%20so%20frustrating.%20The%20past%20year%20has%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20crying%20out%20of%20frustration%20because%20I%20know%20I'm%20capable%20of%20doing%20a%20great%20job%2C%20but%20nobody's%20giving%20me%20the%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%20what%20the%20future%20will%20hold%2C%20so%20I've%20been%20putting%20more%20energy%20into%20my%20happy%20place%20%E2%80%94%20my%20husband%20and%20my%20entertainment%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-lucrative-side-hustles-tried-no-experience-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eside%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20we've%20had%20since%202018%2C%20and%20in%20the%20past%20year%2C%20we've%20focused%20on%20getting%20more%20clients.%20It%20doesn't%20replace%20my%20old%20salary%2C%20but%20it's%20something%20of%20our%20own%2C%20and%20we%20get%20to%20bring%20joy%20to%20other%20people%20through%20our%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2203ce1a41-ba9d-46b6-bf74-ef3be66fe9cb%5C%22%3EMany%20older%20people%20simply%20want%20to%20continue%20doing%20what%20they%20love%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wish%20hiring%20managers%20knew%20that%20many%20older%20people%20just%20want%20the%20chance%20to%20keep%20doing%20what%20they're%20doing%20and%20pass%20along%20their%20experience%20to%20the%20younger%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20to%20other%2050-somethings%20is%20if%20you%20can't%20get%20back%20into%20your%20career%2C%20find%20something%20else%20that%20brings%20joy%20to%20others%20in%20the%20meantime.%20Through%20my%20entertainment%20company%2C%20I've%20found%20that%20bringing%20happiness%20to%20others%20makes%20life%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20give%20up.%20If%20you%20stay%20positive%20and%20focused%20on%20your%20next%20step%2C%20each%20day%20will%20be%20better.%20Even%20though%20we're%20in%20our%2050s%2C%20we're%20not%20done%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20navigating%20a%20career%20change%20in%20your%2050s%3F%20If%20so%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20reporter%20at%20tmartinelli%40businessinsider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-at-56-took-60-percent-pay-cut-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783854361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a511133daf4d560957bef1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-at-56-took-60-percent-pay-cut-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2057-year-old%20accepted%20a%20role%20with%20a%2060%25%20pay%20cut%20after%20struggling%20in%20the%20job%20hunt%20post-layoff.%20She%20is%20budgeting%20and%20downsizing%20while%20job-searching.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmartinelli%40businessinsider.com%20(Tess%20Martinelli)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Violations%20of%20law'%3A%20Vietnam%20arrests