r%20in%20her%20hand.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a50cca0d3a449ec344601dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22860%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELee%20is%20Corgi's%20Head%20of%20Brand.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Erika%20Lee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsun-valley-fashion-sunglasses-shades-alex-karp-karlie-kloss-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESan%20Francisco%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there's%20a%20strong%20sense%20that%20AI%20is%20transforming%20the%20city%20and%20a%20level%20of%20intensity%20that%20I%20don't%20think%20people%20outside%20the%20Bay%20Area%20fully%20appreciate.%20Everyone%20here%20believes%20they're%20early%20to%20something%20massive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEveryday%2C%20I%20meet%20people%20who've%20moved%20across%20state%20and%20city%20lines%20to%20work%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-san-francisco-worth-it-cost-of-living-negativity-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estartups%20in%20San%20Francisco%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Like%20me%2C%20they're%20willing%20to%20make%20extraordinary%20sacrifices%20for%20the%20possibility%20of%20being%20part%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearly-backer-openai-and-anthropic-is-now-betting-on-wellness-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enext%20OpenAI%20or%20Anthropic%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20LA%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20questions%20people%20would%20ask%20me%20at%20events%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20your%20Instagram%3F%26quot%3B%20Conversations%20often%20orbited%20around%20who%20you%20knew%2C%20what%20parties%20you%20were%20invited%20to%2C%20and%20how%20well%20you've%20curated%20yourself%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20San%20Francisco%2C%20online%20curation%20still%20matters%2C%20but%20in%20a%20different%20way.%20People%20ask%20for%20your%20LinkedIn%20or%20X%20account.%20Or%20sometimes%20they%20skip%20social%20media%20entirely%20and%20ask%2C%20%26