20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Kalshi%20advertisement%20on%20a%20Metro%20train%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a51501bdaf4d560957bf7be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Roosevelt%20Institute%20published%20a%20report%20that%20said%20ordinary%20Kalshi%20users%20have%20lost%20almost%20%24600%20million.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20think%20tank%20said%20regular%20people%20are%20unknowingly%20up%20against%20pro%20traders%20and%20big%20firms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKalshi%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20study%20%26quot%3Brests%20on%20a%20methodological%20error.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20New%20York%20City-based%20think%20tank%20says%20regular%20people%20betting%20on%20the%20prediction%20market%20Kalshi%20have%20lost%20almost%20%24600%20million%20as%20they%20unknowingly%20go%20up%20against%20pro%20traders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalshi%20on%20Friday%20hit%20back%20at%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20Roosevelt%20Institute%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frooseveltinstitute.org%2Fblog%2Fsince-kalshis-launch-ordinary-users-have-lost-half-a-billion-dollars%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecently%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20first%20part%20of%20a%20study%20on%20how%20regular%20Kalshi%20users%20have%20fared%20since%20the%20prediction%20site%20was%20launched%20in%202018.%20According%20to%20study's%20co-author%2C%20Brad%20Lipton%2C%20retail%20traders%20have%20lost%20%24583.5%20million%20in%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalshi%20disputes%20the%20group's%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20'house'%20on%20Kalshi%2C%20hidden%20or%20otherwise%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.kalshi.com%2Fp%2Fno-ordinary-users-arent-losing-half-a-billion-dollars-on-kalshi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20a%20response%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20title%20of%20the%20think%20tank's%20report%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Hidden%20House%3A%20Prediction%20Markets%20and%20How%20They're%20Shaping%20Society.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKalshi%20works%20by%20matching%20orders%20together%2C%20like%20all%20financial%20exchanges%20do.%20The%20implication%20that%20there%20could%20be%20a%20'house'%20on%20a%20prediction%20market%20demonstrates%20a%20fundamental%20misunderstanding%20of%20the%20operation%20of%20financial%20exchanges.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20response%20goes%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20study%20%26quot%3Bfalsely%20insinuates%20that%20a%20skill%20gap%20among%20users%20is%20equivalent%20to%20a%20fundamental%20difference%20in%20market%20structure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalshi%20has%20hit%20back%20at%20similar%20claims%20before%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20differentiate%20prediction%20markets%20from%20traditional%20gambling.%20But%20Lipton%2C%20who%20serves%20as%20the%20Roosevelt%20Institute's%20director%20of%20corporate%20power%20and%20financial%20regulation%2C%20says%20that%20regular%20traders%20are%20at%20a%20disadvantage%20without%20knowing%20who's%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20their%20bets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20think%20tank's%20report%20claims%20that%20everyday%20users%20are%20often%20up%20against%20%26quot%3Bprofessional%20traders%20using%20sophisticated%20methods.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrediction%20markets%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprediction-market-event-analysis-outlook-polymarket-insider-trading-market-manipulation-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecome%20under%20fire%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20insider%20trading%20and%20manipulation%20recently.%20Meanwhile%2C%20researchers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpolymarket-informed-insider-trades-study-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehave%20found%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20on%20Kalshi%20rival%20Polymarket%2C%20%26quot%3Binformed%26quot%3B%20traders%20with%20unfair%20advantages%20have%20made%20%24143%20million%20in%20%26quot%3Banomalous%26quot%3B%20profits%20since%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalshi%20has%20emphasized%20that%20it%20is%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshi-suspends-political-candidates-trading-elections-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20taking%20steps%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20ban%20insider%20activity%2C%20though%20Lipton%20says%20he%20is%20not%20convinced%20that%20the%20playing%20field%20is%20even.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20isn't%20clear%20how%20well%20those%20rules%20are%20really%20being%20enforced%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BBut%20there's%20very%20little%20in%20terms%20of%20transparency%20about%20who%20you're%20betting%20against.%20They%20are%20affirmatively%20making%20these%20marketing%20claims%20that%20there's%20no%20house%2C%20and%20that%2C%20to%20me%2C%20is%20misleading.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group's%20report%20largely%20aligns%20with%20an%20investigation%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ffinance%2Finvesting%2Fpolymarket-kalshi-betting-profits-prediction-markets-eb23ac11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%20that%20found%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20users%20on%20both%20Kalshi%20and%20Polymarket%20lose%20money%2C%20and%20that%20most%20of%20the%20profits%20that%20are%20paid%20out%20go%20to%20an%20extremely%20small%20number%20of%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalshi%20maintains%2C%20though%2C%20that%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20Roosevelt%20Institute's%20study%20is%20the%20result%20of%20a%20miscalculation%2C%20one%20that%20compromises%20its%20claim%20that%20retail%20traders%20on%20the%20platform%20have%20lost%20almost%20almost%20%24600%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Kalshi%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Brests%20on%20a%20methodological%20error%20that%20counts%20high-frequency%20trades%20from%20institutional%20market%20makers%20as%20activity%20from%20'ordinary%20users%2C'%20and%20counts%20ordinary%20trades%20from%20casual%20users%20on%20the%20app%20as%20'professional%20users.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshi-who-makes-money-losses-profits-prediction-markets-roosevelt-institute-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783849201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5150239d0a41df475c8f54%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshi-who-makes-money-losses-profits-prediction-markets-roosevelt-institute-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kalshi%20hit%20back%20at%20a%20report%20from%20a%20think%20tank%20that%20says%20ordinary%20users%20are%20getting%20crushed%20on%20the%20site%20as%20they%20unknowingly%20go%20up%20against%20pro%20traders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sobrient%40insider.com%20(Samuel%20O'Brient)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BCCI%20discussing%20Doeschate%20%26amp%3Bamp%3B%20Morne%20Morkel's%20future%20as%20India%20coaches%3B%20T%20Dilip%20under%20fire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783848633000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132343486%2Cimgsize-826960.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fbcci-discusses-ryan-ten-doeschate-and-morne-morkels-future-as-team-india-coaches-t-dilip-under-fire%2Farticleshow%2F132343445.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20cricket%20board%20may%20need%20new%20support%20staff%20after%20England%20tour%20concludes.%20Assistant%20coach%20Ryan%20ten%20Doeschate%20and%20fast%20bowling%20coach%20Morne%20Morkel%20are%20considering%20leaving.%20VVS%20Laxman%20will%20lead%20a%20separate%20coaching%20team%20for%20the%20Zimbabwe%20serie