m%2Fkate-spade-wants-coach-bag-moment-with-gen-z-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKate%20Spade%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20doing%20that%20for%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20to%20go%20all%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20quit%2C%20some%20people%20at%20work%20looked%20at%20me%20like%20I%20had%20three%20heads%20when%20I%20told%20them%20why%20I%20was%20leaving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20we%20have%20a%20portfolio%20with%20eight%20homes%2C%20a%20growing%20mentorship%20business%2C%20and%20two%20children%20whom%20I%20get%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22262b1d51-9d08-498b-be8b-bd4f8c592ed9%5C%22%3EMy%20path%20to%20Wall%20Street%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20my%20work%20ethic%20from%20my%20mom.%20Even%20though%20the%20bus%20fare%20was%20a%20quarter%20or%20two%2C%20my%20mom%20would%20get%20up%20early%20and%20walk%20to%20work%20so%20they%20could%20save%20up%20money%20to%20buy%20a%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscientist-federal-funds-held-trump-fire-employees-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUC%20San%20Diego%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstudent-loans%2Fwhat-is-pell-grant%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPell%20Grants%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20worked%20odd%20jobs.%20My%20first%20job%20after%20school%20was%20as%20an%20insurance%20adjuster%20with%20State%20Fund%2C%20the%20state-sponsored%20workers'%20comp%20carrier%2C%20but%20I%20had%20aspirations%20to%20work%20in%20the%20financial%20markets.%20At%2024%2C%20I%20took%20a%20temp%20job%20off%20Craigslist%20at%20a%20proxy%20research%20firm%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglass-lewis-tells-tesla-investors-reject-elon-musks-1t-pay-2025-10%3Futm_campaign%3Dbusiness-sf%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dlinkedin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGlass%20Lewis%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20had%20recently%20been%20founded%20in%20San%20Francisco%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglass-lewis-tells-tesla-investors-reject-elon-musks-1t-pay-2025-10%3Futm_campaign%3Dbusiness-sf%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dlinkedin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20parents%20asked%20what%20I%20was%20doing%2C%20since%20it%20was%20a%20pay%20cut%2C%20but%20I%20explained%20that%20this%20was%20my%20path%20to%20investment%20banking.%20Eventually%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20some%20mentors%2C%20it%20paid%20off.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20started%20banking%20full-time%20in%202009%20after%20graduating%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcornell-sc-johnson-college-business-mba-investment-banking-immersion-class-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECornell's%20Business%20School%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20the%20most%20money%20I'd%20ever%20made.%20I%20was%20working%20on%20multi-billion-dollar%20deals%20that%20I'd%20see%20in%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%20flying%20business%20class%2C%20and%20staying%20in%20nice%20hotels.%20Exactly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestment-banker-lavish-spending-freedom-satisfaction-retirement-fire-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhat%20you%20think%20investment%20banking%20is%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20wanted%20more.%20I%20saw%20how%20disruptive%20the%20career%20could%20be%20for%20my%20colleagues'%20families%3A%20kids%20in%20boarding%20school%20and%20a%20spouse%20in%20a%20different%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20colleague%20of%20mine%20was%20turning%20comments%20on%20a%20board%20deck%20while%20his%20first%20child%20was%20being%20delivered%2C%20and%20was%20back%20at%20the%20office%20the%20next%20day%20for%20the%20deal.%20And%20I%20remember%20thinking%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20the%20job.%20That's%20what%20it%20asks%20of%20you%20if%20you%20want%20to%20win%20in%20this%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20only%20get%20your%20kid's%20first%20moments%20once%2C%20and%20the%20deal%20will%20always%20be%20there%20asking%20you%20to%20miss%20them.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20the%20guy%20who%20made%20that%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fa9888a0-68bd-49db-b72a-2321595f2899%5C%22%3EWalking%20away%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20my%20mid-30s%2C%20I'd%20saved%20enough%20money%20that%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20get%20married%20and%20start%20a%20family.%20But%20well%20before%20our%20wedding%2C%20my%20wife%2C%20Elizabeth%2C%20and%20I%20were%20trying%20different%20side%20hustles%20to%20build%20a%20business%20that%20could%20eventually%20give%20us%20more%20control%20over%20our%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20married%20a%20banker%2C%20but%20she%20was%20willing%20to%20take%20a%20step%20back%20to%20take%20two%20steps%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20didn't%20need%20to%20be%20an%20investment%20banker%20to%20understand%20that%20cashflowing%20%2410%2C000%20a%20month%20on%20an%20apartment%20with%20a%20%242%2C500%20monthly%20lease%20and%20%241%2C500%20of%20monthly%20expenses%20was%20pretty%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20kept%20growing%20that%20business%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20after%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20of%20sacrificing%20nights%20and%20weekends%20to%20build%20our%20portfolio%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20quit%20my%20job%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20did%2C%20one%20managing%20director%20could%20not%20process%20it%20when%20I%20told%20him%20%E2%80%94he%20froze%20like%20a%20computer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20bump%20in%20the%20road%20was%20COVID.%20After%20everything%20shut%20down%2C%20we%20lost%20all%20of%20our%20bookings%20but%20still%20had%20to%20pay%20rent%20on%20our%20apartments.%20For%20a%20moment%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20business%20we%20had%20been%20building%20for%20years%20was%20over%20and%20I%20might%20have%20to%20return%20to%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20rebuilt%2C%20and%20later%20that%20year%2C%20we%20bought%20our%20first%20property%20in%20the%20Smoky%20Mountains%20of%20Tennessee%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20short-term%20rental%20tax%20benefits.%20We%20now%20have%20eight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225568%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tennessee's%20Great%20Smoky%20Mountains%20National%20Park.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a515233daf4d560957bf81e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETennessee's%20Great%20Smoky%20Mountains%20National%20Park.%3Cp%3EPatrick%20Gorski%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20three%20years%20to%20get%20back%20on%20track%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestment-banker-compensation-salary-bonus-survey-associates-mds-boutiques-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efinancially%20from%20where%20we%20were%20when%20I%20quit%20banking%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20so%20many%20questions%20about%20how%20I%20got%20out%20of%20banking%20while%20living%20in%20New%20York%20with%20two%20kids%2C%20we%20started%20a%20short-term%20rental%20mentorship%20business%20in%202023%20called%20STR%20like%20the%20Best%2C%20along%20with%20a%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvacation-rental-tax-break-big-beautiful-bill-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOne%20Big%20Beautiful%20Bill%20made%20bonus%20depreciation%20permanent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20launched%20a%20homebuying%20program%20buoyed%20by%20the%20tax%20benefit.%20We've%20since%20helped%20over%20100%20of%20our%20clients%20purchase%20an%20investment%20property%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce51dfff-6386-4856-a1d2-08819dba4c7c%5C%22%3EWhy%20it%20was%20worth%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20summer%2C%20I'm%20spending%20seven%20weeks%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-travels-us-taiwan-send-kids-summer-camp-chinese-immersion-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETaiwan%20bringing%20my%20two%20children%20to%20summer%20camp%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20visiting%20my%20wife's%20parents%20while%20still%20running%20our%20business.%20I%20never%20could%20have%20done%20this%20as%20an%20investment%20banker.%20I%20would%20have%20dropped%20them%20off%2C%20given%20them%20a%20hug%2C%20and%20then%20not%20seen%20them%20for%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20parents%20are%20older%20now%2C%20and%20I%20can%20spend%20more%20time%20in%20San%20Francisco%20to%20help%20take%20care%20of%20them.%20I%20see%20it%20as%20a%20small%20way%20to%20pay%20back%20what%20they%20did%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20a%20banker%2C%20you're%20optimized%20for%20the%20firm.%20They%20control%20your%20calendar.%20Now%20I%20can%20optimize%20for%20my%20family.%20The%20business%20is%20a%20means%20to%20fund%20our%20own%20personal%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjunior-bankers-work-hours-shiber-centerview-wall-street-lawsuit-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvestment%20banking%2C%20you're%20never%20off%20the%20clock%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20the%20same%20with%20entrepreneurship.%20But%20now%20I%20own%20all%20the%20upside%20and%20downside%20of%20my%20decision%20here.%20I%20didn't%20want%20someone%20else%20to%20decide%20the%20outcome%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20miss%20the%20intellectual%20firepower%20of%20colleagues%20and%20the%20clients%20I%20worked%20with.%20I%20learned%20a%20ton%20from%20banking.%20It%20made%20me%20a%20much%20better%20businessman%20by%20working%20alongside%20some%20of%20the%20smartest%20CEOs%20and%20operators%20in%20these%20large%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20something%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkeanu-reeves-greatest-person-ever-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKeanu%20Reeves%20said%20on%20Colbert%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20resonated%20with%20me%20more%20than%20any%20other%20quote.%20Colbert%20asked%20him%20what%20happens%20when%20you%20die%2C%20and%20Reeves%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20the%20ones%20who%20love%20us%20will%20miss%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20really%20stuck%20with%20me.%20Your%20money%20is%20not%20going%20to%20miss%20you.%20Your%20kids%2C%20your%20wife%2C%20your%20family%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20my%20parents%2C%20my%20mom%20is%20no%20longer%20able%20to%20say%20her%20son%20works%20at%20a%20big%20bank.%20She%20instead%20says%20that%20her%20son%20went%20to%20Cornell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20that%20they've%20seen%20how%20much%20time%20we%20spend%20with%20our%20family%2C%20they've%20come%20around%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-investment-banking-career-vacation-rentals-fatherhood-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783848301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a514cc9d9d92978fe6a6083%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-investment-banking-career-vacation-rentals-fatherhood-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20banker%20explains%20why%20he%20left%20Wall%20Street%20%E2%80%94%20disappointing%20his%20immigrant%20parents%20%E2%80%94%20to%20build%20a%20vacation-rental%20business.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22anicoll%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Nicoll)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shiv%20Panditt%20heaps%20praise%20on%20Jason%20Sanjay'%20'Sigma'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783848089000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132343266%2Cimgsize-168848.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fshiv-panditt-heaps-praise-on-debutant-director-jason-sanjay-sigma-ahead-of-making-a-comeback-in-tamil-cinema-after-14-years-he-kno