4e63c8d3b3e45765196888%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224519%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOngoing%20lawsuits%20are%20pushing%20to%20block%20some%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20student-loan%20changes.%3Cp%3EAlex%20WROBLEWSKI%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESeveral%20of%20Trump's%20student-loan%20repayment%20changes%20took%20effect%20July%201.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOngoing%20lawsuits%20blocked%20key%20provisions%20from%20taking%20effect%2C%20including%20a%20narrowed%20definition%20of%20professional%20degree.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPublic%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20and%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20are%20also%20the%20subject%20of%20litigation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EKey%20provisions%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20sweeping%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-repayment-overhaul-what-to-expect-july-1-trump-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estudent-loan%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20landed%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20administration's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Enew%20repayment%20plans%20and%20borrowing%20caps%20took%20effect%20July%201%2C%20other%20elements%20did%20not%2C%20including%20a%20narrower%20definition%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bprofessional%26quot%3B%20degree%20and%20limits%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-could-lose-pslf-debt-forgiveness-new-limits-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPublic%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%3C%2Fa%3E%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20for%20months%2C%20borrowers%20and%20advocacy%20groups%20have%20been%20fighting%20those%20changes%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20court.%20They%20argued%20that%20some%20of%20the%20administration's%20student-loan%20plans%20are%20unlawful%20and%20are%20asking%20courts%20to%20pause%20implementation%20before%20blocking%20the%20provisions%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20battles%20come%20as%20millions%20of%20federal%20borrowers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-higher-monthly-payments-retirement-jobs-debt-trump-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebrace%20for%20higher%20monthly%20bills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20under%20the%20looming%20threat%20of%20default%20and%20its%20consequences%2C%20such%20as%20wage%20garnishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20will%20Trump's%20student-loan%20changes%20affect%20you%3F%20Are%20you%20preparing%20for%20higher%20monthly%20payments%20or%20changing%20your%20educational%20plans%3F%20Share%20your%20story%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F7Td2yVsmvM31yKsT6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilling%20out%20this%20form%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20we'll%20be%20in%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ab6295c5-9cd8-458e-9e13-92af51021af3%5C%22%3EWhere%20student-loan%20lawsuits%20stand%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22274c8e93-19d3-411e-b175-8302d372b577%5C%22%3EBorrowing%20caps%20for%20professional%20degrees%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2024%2C%20US%20District%20Judge%20Beryl%20Howell%20blocked%20the%20Education%20Department%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcourt-blocks-student-loan-borrowing-caps-nurses-trump-repayment-overhaul-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eimplementing%20its%20narrowed%20definition%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20professional%20degree%2C%20which%20it%20had%20planned%20to%20roll%20out%20on%20July%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20definition%20would%20have%20allowed%2011%20programs%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20higher%20%24200%2C000%20lifetime%20borrowing%20cap%20for%20professional%20degrees%2C%20while%20excluding%20programs%20like%20advanced%20nursing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20held%20that%20the%20administration's%20plan%20was%20unlawful%20and%20would%20exacerbate%20the%20healthcare%20worker%20shortage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETyler%20Smith%2C%20the%20chief%20policy%20officer%20at%20the%20PA%20Education%20Association%2C%20a%20plaintiff%2C%20said%20that%20while%20the%20pause%20is%20encouraging%2C%20a%20final%20decision%20in%20the%20case%20is%20still%20pending%2C%20prolonging%20uncertainty%20for%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20difficult%20time%20for%20applicants%20and%20programs%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20plan%2C%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20have%20stable%20cohorts%2C%20that%20they'll%20be%20able%20to%20complete%20their%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20case%20proceeds%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20has%20released%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnurses-higher-student-loan-limits-trump-debt-repayment-overhaul-caps-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eupdated%20list%20of%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20will%20meet%20the%20definition%20of%20a%20professional%20degree%20and%20qualify%20for%20the%20higher%20borrowing%20cap%2C%20including%20advanced%20nursing%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20interim%20administrative%20designations%20are%20provided%20solely%20to%20facilitate%20implementation%20of%20the%20Court's%20order%20and%20may%20change%20as%20litigation%20in%20the%20case%20proceeds%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20department's%20guidance%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cb0d0387-6d1f-4d63-9e36-3f93d976ffc2%5C%22%3EPublic%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%20before%20it%20was%20set%20to%20take%20effect%2C%20two%20federal%20judges%20blocked%20the%20Education%20Department's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-plan-to-limit-pslf-student-loan-forgiveness-is-blocked-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erule%20to%20limit%20eligibility%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20program%2C%20which%20forgives%20student%20debt%20for%20government%20and%20nonprofit%20workers%20after%2010%20years%20of%20qualifying%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rule%2C%20which%20the%20department%20finalized%20late%20last%20year%2C%20would%20have%20stripped%20PSLF%20eligibility%20from%20employers%20that%20the%20administration%20determined%20did%20not%20meet%20its%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20service%26quot%3B%20definition%2C%20such%20as%20those%20that%20supported%20gender-affirming%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rule%20prompted%20lawsuits%20from%20nonprofits%20and%20advocacy%20groups%20that%20argued%20the%20rule%20was%20an%20overreach%20of%20the%20administration's%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20courts%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWinston%20Berkman-Breen%2C%20legal%20director%20at%20advocacy%20group%20and%20plaintiff%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EProtect%20Borrowers%2C%20said%20the%20Education%20Department's%20options%20are%20to%20appeal%20the%20ruling%20or%20move%20on%2C%20and%20he's%20%26quot%3Bconfident%20that%20the%20program%20will%20continue%20as%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rule%20was%20%26quot%3Barbitrary%20and%20capricious%20and%20doesn't%20really%20provide%20enough%20rationale%20or%20clarity%20to%20folks%2C%26quot%3B%20Berkman-Breen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUndersecretary%20of%20Education%20Nicholas%20Kent%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20in%20response%20to%20the%20ruling%20that%20the%20department%20%26quot%3Bstands%20behind%20this%20commonsense%20policy%20to%20ensure%20that%20taxpayer%20dollars%20are%20never%20used%20to%20subsidize%20illegal%20activities%20and%20is%20evaluating%20next%20steps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKent%20also%20said%20during%20a%20summit%20at%20the%20department%20on%20July%207%20that%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Inspector%20General%20is%20conducting%20a%20%26quot%3Bthorough%20review%26quot%3B%20of%20PSLF%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228405d3dd-76a7-4a30-826b-742afdc08400%5C%22%3EThe%20SAVE%20Plan%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20announced%20a%20settlement%20that%20eliminated%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Biden-era%20repayment%20scheme%20that%20allowed%20for%20cheaper%20payments%20%E2%80%94%20in%20March.%20Beginning%20July%201%2C%20servicers%20began%20notifying%20SAVE%20borrowers%20of%20their%2090-day%20timeframe%20to%20transition%20to%20a%20new%20repayment%20plan%2C%20or%20be%20automatically%20moved%20to%20the%20most%20expensive%20repayment%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20an%20ongoing%20lawsuit%20that's%20pushing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-lawsuit-stop-transfer-student-loan-borrowers-repayment-trump-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estop%20the%20forced%20transition%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20SAVE%20borrowers%20to%20a%20different%20repayment%20plan.%20On%20June%2023%2C%20the%20law%20firm%20Public%20Goods%20Practice%20asked%20a%20federal%20court%20to%20stop%20the%20department%20from%20involuntarily%20moving%20borrowers%20to%20a%20new%20repayment%20plan%20while%20the%20lawsuit%20proceeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20argues%20that%2C%20with%20SAVE%20eliminated%2C%20the%20department%20must%20make%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20earlier%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EREPAYE%20plan%20available%20to%20borrowers.%20A%20department%20spokesperson%20disputed%20the%20claims%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20and%20encouraged%20borrowers%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20new%20Repayment%20Assistance%20Plan%2C%20which%20became%20available%20on%20July%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20student%20loans%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3A%2520asheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawsuits-student-loan-debt-relief-borrowers-repayment-overhaul-save-pslf-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783847701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F