%20in%20Japan%20Airlines'%20retro%20'JAL%20Suite'%20first-class%20cabin.%20These%204%20things%20surprised%20me%20the%20most.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20in%20the%20Japan%20Airlines'%20retro%20%26quot%3BJAL%20Suite%26quot%3B%20with%20his%20toddler.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a510ced9d0a41df475c85e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221501%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20flew%20in%20Japan%20Airlines'%20retro%20%26quot%3BJAL%20Suite%26quot%3B%20with%20my%20wife%20and%20toddler%20for%2010%20hours%20and%20it%20was%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20flights%20yet.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20T.J.%20Dunn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20flew%20first%20class%20on%20Japan%20Airlines'%20%26quot%3BJAL%20Suite%26quot%3B%20from%20Sydney%20to%20Tokyo%20in%20January%202026.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20more%20than%20a%20decade-old%20cabin%20was%20surprisingly%20comfortable%20with%20great%20amenities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%2013-course%20meal%20and%20top-shelf%20Champagne%20and%20whisky%20were%20outstanding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20experienced%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20luxurious%20premium%20cabins%20as%20airlines%20race%20to%20pack%20in%20ever%20more%20cutting-edge%20amenities%20at%2035%2C000%20feet.%20But%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-airlines-business-class-flight-review-drawbacks-worth-it-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflying%20Japan%20Airlines'%3C%2Fa%3E%20retro%20flagship%20first-class%20cabin%2C%20I'm%20convinced%20that%20old-school%20luxury%20can%20still%20compete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20of%20three%20flew%20the%20airline's%20%26quot%3BJAL%20Suite%26quot%3B%20for%2010%20hours%20from%20Sydney%20to%20Tokyo%20in%20January%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20named%20a%20five-star%20airline%20by%20the%20aviation%20ranking%20website%20Skytrax%2C%20I%20expected%20exceptional%20comfort%2C%20food%2C%20and%20service%20%E2%80%94%20and%20nearly%20every%20part%20of%20the%20experience%20delivered%2C%20from%20the%20airport%20lounge%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-first-class-flying-has-changed-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etop-shelf%20Champagne%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20elaborate%20multi-course%20inflight%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20most%20impressed%20me%20was%20how%20well%20Japan%20Airlines'%20aging%20cabin%20has%20held%20up.%20Despite%20lacking%20doors%2C%20its%20open%20layout%20made%20flying%20with%20a%20toddler%20much%20easier%20and%20it%20was%20still%20perfectly%20private%20and%20cozy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20introduced%20in%202008%20and%20refreshed%20in%202013%2C%20the%20JAL%20Suite%20is%20exclusive%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-airlines-ceo-pay-cut-workers-misconduct-japan-corporate-culture-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJapan%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E'%20Boeing%20777-300ER%20fleet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20those%20aircraft%20are%20gradually%20replaced%20by%20the%20modern%20Airbus%20A350%2C%20the%20cabin%20will%20eventually%20be%20phased%20out%20in%20favor%20of%20a%20new%20pod-style%20suite%20with%20doors%20%E2%80%94%20though%20Japan%20Airlines%20has%20not%20announced%20an%20official%20retirement%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20surprised%20me%20most%20about%20flying%20Japan%20Airlines'%20iconic%20JAL%20Suite.%20I%20paid%20about%20113%2C000%20airline%20points%20for%20the%20three%20one-way%20tickets%3B%20cash%20fares%20can%20cost%20up%20to%20%2410%2C000%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a261c1a7-7857-4f5e-bd58-9ae27b246392%5C%22%3EI%20accessed%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20best%20airport%20lounges%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-airline-in-the-world-japan-singapore-ranking-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJapan%20Airlines%20is%20a%3C%2Fa%3E%20member%20of%20the%20oneworld%20alliance%2C%20giving%20eligible%20first-class%20passengers%20access%20to%20premium%20lounges%20operated%20by%20other%20alliance%20members%20before%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20our%20flight%2C%20that%20meant%20my%20family%20could%20relax%20in%20the%20ultra-luxe%20Qantas%20International%20First%20Lounge%20in%20Sydney.%20It%20consistently%20receives%20excellent%20reviews%20from%20flyers%20and%20was%20named%20one%20of%20the%20top%2010%20first-class%20airline%20lounges%20by%20Skytrax%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221260%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Qantas%20lounge%20in%20Sydney.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5106559d0a41df475c8556%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22945%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Qantas%20lounge%20had%20a%20great%20view%20of%20the%20tarmac.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20T.J.%20Dunn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20visited%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fqantas-airlines-offers-luxury-features-for-travelers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQantas%20First%3C%2Fa%3E%20Lounge%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20which%20gave%20me%20a%20pretty%20good%20idea%20of%20what%20to%20expect%3A%20great%20food%2C%20unique%20design%2C%20and%20premium%20amenities.%20However%2C%20the%20Sydney%20location%20exceeded%20my%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20retro%20flap-board%20information%20displays%2C%20the%20panoramic%20views%20of%20the%20tarmac%20and%20the%20Sydney%20skyline%2C%20the%20fantastic%20breakfast%20and%20coffee%2C%20and%20the%20generous%20seating%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20the%20premium%20experience%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221260%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20and%20son%20in%20front%20of%20the%20old-timey%20departures%20flip%20board%20at%20the%20Qantas%20lounge.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a51068e9d0a41df475c855a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22945%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20loved%20the%20flap-board.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20T.J.%20Dunn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20only%20frustration%20was%20that%20the%20lounge's%20spa%20%E2%80%94%20which%20offers%20complimentary%20treatments%20for%20guests%20%E2%80%94%20didn't%20have%20any%20appointments%20available%20until%20after%20our%20flight%20departed%2C%20even%20though%20we%20arrived%20four%20hours%20before%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-class-comparison-qantas-singapore-american-airlines-which-is-best-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20flight%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20only%20blemish%20on%20an%20otherwise%20excellent%20pre-departure%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d90a5842-417d-4f0d-9429-ee13781e2237%5C%22%3EThe%2013-year-old%20cabin%20is%20impressive%20despite%20its%20age%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20Airlines%20offers%20two%20first-class%20products%3A%20the%20older%20configuration%20on%20its%20777-300ERs%2C%20and%20the%20new%20cabin%20%E2%80%94%20complete%20with%20sliding%20doors%20and%20updated%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-qantas-custom-a350-built-for-the-worlds-longest-flight-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirbus%20A350-1000s%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20JAL%20Suite%20is%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20old%2C%20I%20expected%20it%20to%20feel%20worn%20and%20dated.%20Instead%2C%20its%20wood-paneled%20interior%20and%20oversized%20leather%20loungers%20felt%20warm%20and%20inviting.%20The%20seats%20were%20in%20excellent%20condition%2C%20and%20settling%20into%20one%20felt%20like%20sinking%20into%20a%20leather%20La-Z-Boy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221309%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20family%20in%20the%20JAL%20Suite.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5106f4d9d92978fe6a572b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22872%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20JAL%20Suite%20in%20configured%20in%20a%201x2x1%20layout%2C%20so%20everyone%20has%20aisle%20access.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20T.J.%20Dunn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20partition%20lowered%20between%20our%20two%20adjacent%20seats%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20cabin%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20could%20easily%20share%20parental%20duties%20without%20any%20gymnastics.%20There%20was%20also%20ample%20storage%20space%20to%20absorb%20toys%2C%20books%2C%20bottles%2C%20and%20the%20general%20chaos%20of%20traveling%20with%20a%20toddler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20time%20to%20rest%2C%20the%20flight%20attendants%20prepared%20the%20spacious%20bed%20with%20a%20cozy%20mattress%20pad%20and%20deluxe%20bedding.%20We%20were%20given%20complimentary%20pajamas%20and%20amenity%20kits%20with%20luxury%20skincare%20and%20toiletry%20products%20from%20Japanese%20beauty%20brands%20Cl%C3%A9%20de%20Peau%20Beaut%C3%A9%20and%20Shiseido.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20collage%20of%20the%20toiletries%20and%20bed%20in%20the%20JAL%20Suite.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a51086edaf4d560957bedcb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20versions%20of%20the%20amenity%20kits%20had%20products%20for%20women%20(Cl%C3%A9%20de%20Peau%20Beaut%C3%A9)%20and%20men%20(Shiseido).%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20T.J.%20Dunn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20expected%20the%20gentle%20steam%20eye%20mask%20to%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20gimmick%2C%20but%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20surprisingly%20pleasant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-airlines-first-class-cabins-airbus-a350-speakers-headrest-photos-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJAL%20Suite%20is%20flying%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20about%20a%20dozen%20routes%2C%20while%20the%20A350%20flies%20between%20Tokyo%20and%20New%20York%2C%20Dallas%2C%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20London%2C%20and%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20Airlines%20has%20not%20yet%20announced%20an%20official%20retirement%20date%20for%20its%20eight%20remaining%20777-300ERs%3B%20five%20have%20left%20the%20fleet%20since%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295adf18a-2d86-4191-b817-0196f6b6aa0a%5C%22%3EJapan%20Airlines'%20top-tier%20Champagne%20isn't%20served%20on%20every%20route%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20Airlines%20is%20known%20for%20serving%20the%20most%20expensive%20Champagne%20in%20commercial%20aviation%3A%20the%20ultra-luxe%20Champagne%20Salon%202015%2C%20which%20retails%20for%20up%20to%20%241%2C500%20a%20bottle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20excited%20to%20try%20it%20on%20this%20flight%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20realize%20until%20a%20few%20days%20before%20departure%20that%20the%20airline's%20beverage%20list%20varies%20by%20route%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Sydney%20wasn't%20one%20of%20the%20routes%20featuring%20the%20rare%20bottle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChampagne%20Salon%202015%20is%20reserved%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-business-class-travel-hack-learned-as-a-parent-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJapan%20Airlines'%20flagship%3C%2Fa%3E%20routes%2C%20like%20Tokyo%20to%20New%20York%20and%20London%2C%20where%20the%20first-class%20wine%20list%20is%20significantly%20more%20elevated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20our%20Sydney-Tokyo%20flight%2C%20the%20Champagne%20was%20Jacquesson%20Cuv%C3%A9e%20%23744%2C%20which%20retails%20for%20around%20%24100%20a%20bottle%2C%20while%20the%20whisky%20selection%20included%20Suntory%20Hibiki%20100th%20Anniversary%2C%20which%20sells%20for%20around%20%24400.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22958%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Champagne%20Jacquesson%20744%20bottle%20next%20to%20the%20glass.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a510ae19d0a41df475c859a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22639%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Champagne%20on%20my%20flight%20was%20Jacquesson%20Cuv%C3%A9e%20%23744.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20T.J.%20Dunn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20were%20excellent%2C%20but%20I%20recommend%20flyers%20check%20the%20beverage%20list%20for%20their%20specific%20route%20before%20booking%20if%20they%20want%20to%20experience%20Salon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ab343f3a-b612-4861-8b52-341b32287d66%5C%22%3EThe%20inflight%20meal%20was%20a%20full%20culinary%20experience%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20Airlines%20has%20earned%20an%20excellent%20reputation%20for%20its%20in-flight%20catering%2C%20especially%20in%20first%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20my%20way%20through%20an%20inflight%20%3Cem%3Ewashoku%20%3C%2Fem%3Efeast%20%E2%80%94%20a%20traditional%20Japanese%20multi-course%20culinary%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20I%20finally%20understood%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%2013%20dishes%20served%20over%20seven%20courses%2C%20plus%20an%20additional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvintage-photos-of-plane-food-2016-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eround%20for%20caviar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20opted%20for%20the%20Japanese%20menu%20instead%20of%20the%20Western%20menu%2C%20and%20enjoyed%20dishes%20such%20as%20miso-marinated%20broccolini%20with%20salmon%20roe%2C%20potato%20potage%20with%20grilled%20cod%20and%20truffle%2C%20and%20roast%20beef%20with%20sansho%20pepper%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20collage%20of%20the%20meals%20on%20JAL%2C%20including%20caviar.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a510c4cd9d92978fe6a579c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20multi-course%20meal%20included%20foods%20like%20caviar%2C%20noodles%2C%20vegetables%2C%20beef%2C%20and%20seafood.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20T.J.%20Dunn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20leather-bound%20menu%20made%20it%20feel%20more%20like%20dining%20at%20a%20restaurant%20rather%20than%20ordering%20on%20a%20plane.%20And%20the%20crew%20was%20attentive%2C%20kind%2C%20and%20extremely%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20post-meal%20nap%2C%20I%20ordered%20a%20few%20items%20from%20the%20%C3%A0%20la%20carte%20menu%3A%20simmered%20Hida%20beef%2C%20rice%20with%20grilled%20scallops%2C%20and%20ramen.%20I%20also%20tried%20the%20airline's%20signature%20non-alcoholic%20drink%2C%20SKY%20TIME.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20served%20was%20excellent%2C%20though%20if%20you're%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20Japanese%20cuisine%2C%20I'd%20recommend%20ordering%20from%20the%20Western%20menu%2C%20which%20includes%20items%20like%20prime%20beef%20tenderloin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20glad%20I%20finally%20got%20to%20experience%20Japan%20Airlines'%20retro%20first%20class%20before%20it%20retires.%20It%20was%20perfect%20for%20my%20family%2C%20and%20the%20generous%20cabin%20size%2C%20attentive%20crew%2C%20and%20exceptional%20food%20made%20it%20one%20of%20the%20more%20memorable%20long-haul%20flights%20I've%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20time%2C%20I'll%20set%20my%20sights%20on%20a%20flagship%20route%20just%20to%20see%20what%20Salon%20tastes%20like%20at%2035%2C000%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-flying-first-class-japan-airlines-jal-suite-review-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783846802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a510ced9d0a41df475c85e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-flying-first-class-japan-airlines-jal-suite-review-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20was%20surprising%20by%20how%20well%20Japan%20Airlines'%20famous%2013-year-old%20cabin%20has%20held%20up%2C%20and%20the%20Japanese%20cuisine%2C%20which%20came%20with%20caviar%2C%20was%20delicious.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(T.J.%20Dunn)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mamdani's%20biggest%20promises%20are%20now%20this%20millennial's%20day%20job%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228835%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Levine%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3ed69a360acd489560c213%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225890%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMamdani%20insider%20Sam%20Levine%20oversees%20all%20workers%20and%20consumers%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3ECorrie%20Aune%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20Levine%20can't%20stand%20a%20ripoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzohran-mamdani-opens-nyc-events-with-lotteries-draws-excitement-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20City's%3C%2Fa%3E%20millennial%20commissioner%20of%20Consumer%20and%20Worker%20Protection.%20The%20former%20lawyer%20%E2%80%94%20who%20worked%20under%20Lina%20Khan%20at%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20%E2%80%94%20said%20he%20didn't%20hesitate%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20department%20this%20spring%20when%20CVS%20sent%20him%20an%20expired%20coupon.%20And%20he%20thinks%20it's%20ludicrous%20that%20his%20halal%20guy%20charged%20him%20more%20than%20%2420%20for%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcan-nyc-mamdani-make-halal-cheaper-we-asked-street-vendors-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost-Knicks%20victory%20meal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20people%20to%20move%20away%20from%20a%20sense%20of%20resignation%20that%20this%20is%20just%20the%20economy%20we're%20stuck%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20move%20toward%20a%20more%20hopeful%20view%20that%20we%20can%20fight%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228210%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Levine%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3ed770a25092c74cca00aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225473%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20different%20protections%20for%20workers%20than%20you%20do%20for%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20Levine%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BBut%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20we're%20talking%20about%20people.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECorrie%20Aune%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELevine%20has%20a%20daunting%20job.%20He%20oversees%20an%20agency%20responsible%20for%20enforcing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsumer-loyalty-dead-airline-miles-internet-company-car-insurance-prices-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efair%20business%20practices%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20five%20boroughs%2C%20home%20to%208.5%20million%20people.%20His%20department%20is%20one%20of%20the%20smallest%20in%20the%20NYC%20government%2C%20with%20about%20400%20employees%20and%20a%20stretched-thin%20budget.%20For%20comparison%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F3-ways-mamdani-plans-to-make-nyc-housing-more-affordable-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20city's%20housing%20authority%3C%2Fa%3E%20employs%20about%2012%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department's%20mission%20is%20central%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmamdani-free-fast-buses-nyc-commuters-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMamdani's%20affordability%20agenda%3C%2Fa%3E.%20DCWP%20is%20one%20of%20City%20Hall's%20main%20arms%20taking%20on%20corporate%20malfeasance%20and%20enforcing%20worker%20protection%20policies.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cityandstateny.com%2Fpersonality%2F2026%2F01%2Fheres-why-you-keep-seeing-mamdanis-consumer-protection-commissioner-everywhere%2F410873%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELocal%20outlet%20City%26amp%3BState%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20a%20story%20in%20January%20with%20the%20headline%20%26quot%3BWhy%20you%20keep%20seeing%20Mamdani's%20consumer%20protection%20commissioner%20everywhere.%26quot%3B%20Cross-legged%20on%20his%20lower%20Manhattan%20office%20couch%2C%20Levine%20told%20me%20that%2C%20historically%2C%20his%20department%20hasn't%20been%20a%20major%20headline-maker.%20He's%20determined%20to%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20June%20evening%2C%20I%20shadowed%20Levine%20at%20an%20event%20celebrating%20fashion%20workers%20and%20addressing%20the%20challenges%20models%20face%20because%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frainbow-shops-fashion-models-ai-use-jobs-impact-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20and%20financial%20insecurity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20soon%20as%20we%20walked%20in%2C%20the%20commissioner%20was%20surrounded%20by%20a%20gaggle%20of%20attendees%2C%20casually%20chatting%20over%20hors%20d'oeuvres%20and%20barely-chilled%20beer%20about%20everything%20from%20the%20weather%20to%20fair%20wages.%20He%20appeared%20to%20have%20the%20same%20combination%20of%20media%20training%20and%20everyman%20relatability%20that's%20become%20a%20trademark%20of%20his%20boss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226230%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Levine%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3ed82ae218c3b62535de94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%228722%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELevine%20gave%20an%20address%20at%20a%20Manhattan%20event%20celebrating%20fashion%20workers.%20Between%20keynotes%2C%20commencements%2C%20and%20events%2C%20he%20gives%20at%20least%20one%20speech%20a%20week.%3Cp%3ECorrie%20Aune%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20not%20everyone%20is%20a%20fan.%20Business%20Insider%20reached%20out%20to%20two%20dozen%20companies%20and%20trade%20associations%20targeted%20by%20Levine's%20actions%20%E2%80%94%20including%20delivery%20apps%2C%20hotels%2C%20restaurants%2C%20retailers%2C%20auto%20dealers%2C%20and%20law%20firms.%20While%20most%20didn't%20reply%2C%20some%20said%20they're%20concerned%20that%20the%20city's%20consumer-focused%20approach%20will%20affect%20their%20bottom%20line.%20And%20white-shoe%20law%20firms%20are%20already%20advising%20clients%20to%20tread%20carefully%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20NYC%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20people%20are%20getting%20frustrated%20at%20every%20turn%20and%20maybe%20feeling%20like%20the%20days%20of%20being%20actually%20able%20to%20speak%20to%20a%20human%20or%20pay%20a%20standard%20price%20are%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20Levine%20said.%20%26quot%3BOne%20message%20I%20really%20want%20people%20to%20know%3A%20This%20is%20not%20inevitable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ELevine's%20phone%20rang%20late%20one%20December%20evening%20as%20he%20and%20his%20partner%20were%20watching%20TV%20in%20their%20apartment.%20It%20was%20an%20unknown%20number.%20He%20missed%20it.%20A%20few%20minutes%20later%2C%20the%20lockscreen%20glowed%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrifying%26quot%3B%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHey%2C%20this%20is%20Mayor-elect%20Zohran%20Mamdani.%20Can%20you%20please%20give%20me%20a%20call%3F%26quot%3B%20Levine%20was%20being%20offered%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20week%2C%20he%20was%20announced%20as%20DCWP%20commissioner%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDSlyGukDgAy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20NFL%20draft-style%20Instagram%20post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228771%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Levine%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3ed808360acd489560c22e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225847%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20shaped%20over%20the%20years%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it's%20New%20York%20City%20or%20Chicago%20or%20Washington%20%E2%80%94%20by%20the%20notion%20that%20government%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20muscular%20champion%20for%20working%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Levine%20said.%3Cp%3ECorrie%20Aune%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20the%20role%2C%20Levine%20earned%20his%20law%20degree%20at%20Harvard%2C%20worked%20as%20an%20attorney%20in%20Illinois%2C%20served%20as%20director%20of%20the%20FTC's%20Bureau%20of%20Consumer%20Protection%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20and%20had%20a%20stint%20in%20academia%20at%20Berkeley.%20Khan%20%E2%80%94%20his%20former%20boss%20and%20a%20chair%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flina-khan-big-tech-acquihire-deals-could-meet-ftc-scrutiny-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMamdani%20transition%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20pitched%20him%20on%20a%20role%20in%20the%20mayor's%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevine's%20office%20has%20since%20taken%20action%20to%20ban%20hidden%20hotel%20fees%2C%20stop%20excessive%20credit%20card%20holds%2C%20crack%20down%20on%20delivery%20app%20exploitation%2C%20promote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firs-direct-file-doge-treasury-department-failed-program-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efree%20tax%20filing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20resolve%20Fair%20Work%20Week%20violations%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffree-trials-consumers-subscription-economy-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduce%20subscription%20traps%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20New%20Yorkers.%20Since%20Levine%20entered%20office%2C%20the%20department%20said%20it%20has%20filed%20major%20lawsuits%20over%20worker%20and%20consumer%20rights%20violations%2C%20sent%20more%20than%20137%2C000%20notices%20to%20businesses%20for%20noncompliance%20with%20NYC%20law%2C%20and%20secured%20over%20%2410%20million%20in%20restitution%2C%20some%20of%20which%20was%20for%20delivery%20and%20fast%20food%20workers%20who%20courts%20found%20were%20denied%20PTO%20or%20predictable%20shifts%20by%20their%20employers.%20This%20work%20builds%20on%20Fair%20Work%20Week%20laws%20and%20gig%20worker%20protection%20efforts%20that%20began%20before%20the%20Mamdani%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226282%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Levine%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3ed7cee218c3b62535de90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%228795%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMuch%20of%20Levine's%20work%20at%20DCWP%20is%20central%20to%20Mamdani's%20affordability%20agenda.%3Cp%3ECorrie%20Aune%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20policy%2C%20Levine%20has%20adopted%20Mamdani's%20social%20media-forward%20communications%20strategy%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20prioritizes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswag-socialism-wait-for-mamdani-affordable-nyc-world-cup-jerseys-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebite-sized%20Instagram%20videos%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20unscripted%20livestreams%20alongside%20traditional%20news%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevine%20famously%20joined%20Mamdani%20for%20a%20live%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fshorts%2Fc12zIyHrVGo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaco%20Bell%20and%20Dunkin'%20lunch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20during%20which%20the%20two%20celebrated%20a%20%241.8%20million%20win%20for%20retail%20and%20food%20workers%20following%20claims%20the%20companies%20violated%20local%20scheduling%20laws.%20At%20the%20Prospect%20Park%20Zoo's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmamdani-nyc-food-delivery-app-fees-crackdown-settlement-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ered%20panda%20exhibit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Levine%20and%20the%20mayor%20announced%20a%20settlement%20requiring%20delivery%20app%20HungryPanda%20to%20pay%20over%20%24875%2C000%20for%20withholding%20minimum%20pay%20from%20employees%2C%20and%20the%20pair%20spent%20a%20recent%20night%20distributing%20Workers'%20Bill%20of%20Rights%20pamphlets%20at%20Brooklyn%20restaurants.%20On%20July%2010%2C%20Levine%20and%20Mamdani%20were%20joined%20by%20Khan%20to%20announce%20the%20administration's%20latest%20click-to-cancel%20rules%20in%20an%20East%20Village%20gym%20%E2%80%94%20the%20podium%20set%20up%20between%20a%20row%20of%20treadmills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELorelei%20Salas%2C%20who%20served%20as%20Bill%20de%20Blasio's%20DCWP%20commissioner%2C%20told%20me%20that%20she%20gives%20Levine%20%26quot%3Ban%20A%2B%26quot%3B%20for%20both%20his%20policy%20and%20outreach%20efforts.%20She%20feels%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Busing%20every%20tool%20at%20his%20disposal%2C%26quot%3B%20even%20if%20that%20means%20doing%20things%20differently%20than%20when%20she%20stepped%20into%20the%20role%20a%20decade%20ago.%20%26quot%3BQuick%20hits%2C%20quick%20videos%3A%20That's%20what's%20grabbing%20people's%20attention%20these%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20great%20to%20see%20that%20DCWP%20is%20actually%20embracing%20that%20way%20of%20communicating%20with%20New%20Yorkers%2C%20informing%20them%20of%20their%20rights.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%229504%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Levine%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3ed7e6360acd489560c22c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226336%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20reach%20fast%20food%20workers%3F%20It's%20not%20with%20a%20press%20release.%26quot%3B%20Levine%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20reach%20people%20where%20they%20are.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECorrie%20Aune%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20am%20proudest%20of%20is%20how%20we've%20made%20ourselves%20a%20visible%20presence%20in%20New%20York%2C%26quot%3B%20Levine%20said.%20As%20he%20sees%20it%2C%20greater%20visibility%20would%20lead%20to%20more%20complaints%2C%20more%20311%20calls%2C%20and%20greater%20compliance%20among%20businesses.%20%26quot%3BEven%20though%20we're%20a%20small%20agency%2C%20we%20are%20not%20afraid%20to%20take%20on%20big%20players.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Levine's%20office%2C%20there's%20a%20vintage%20gold%20scale%20of%20justice%2C%20a%20poster%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzohran-mamdani-rental-ripoff-hearing-bad-landlords-rent-freeze-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BRental%20Ripoff%26quot%3B%20hearings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%20framed%20copy%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Post%20cover%20that%20featured%20his%20and%20Mamdani's%20Taco%20Bell%20Crunchwrap%20feast.%20It%20reads%20%26quot%3BCommie%20and%20Get%20It!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20headline%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Levine%20says%20he%20found%20funny%20%E2%80%94%20hits%20on%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20criticism%20the%20mayor%20and%20his%20cabinet%20have%20heard%20from%20New%20Yorkers%3A%20that%20their%20affordability%20promises%20will%20come%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20Wall%20Street%2C%20discourage%20Big%20Tech%20investment%2C%20or%20cause%20an%20eventual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinance-world-memes-reaction-zohran-mamdani-new-york-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexodus%20of%20the%20ultrawealthy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%229442%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rental%20Ripoff%20Hearing%20poster%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3ed6ffa25092c74cca0099%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226295%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELevine%20has%20appeared%20alongside%20Mamdani%20at%20many%20public%20events%20focused%20on%20rental%20ripoffs%2C%20subscription%20traps%2C%20Fair%20Work%20Week%20laws%2C%20and%20more.%3Cp%3ECorrie%20Aune%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20commissioner%20has%20an%20ambitious%20agenda%2C%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMamdani%20recently%20pledged%20another%20%244.3%20million%20to%20the%20department%20to%20%26quot%3Bexpand%20capacity%20for%20DCWP%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20plans%20to%20grow%20that%20additional%20funding%20to%20%2418%20million%20annually%20in%20fiscal%20year%202029.%20The%20department's%20fiscal%20year%202027%20budget%20is%20approximately%20%2478.5%20million.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPlenty%20of%20affordability%20issues%2C%20like%20minimum%20wage%20laws%20and%20NYC's%20steep%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20are%20also%20outside%20Levine's%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevine%20said%20his%20strategy%20is%20centered%20on%20holding%20corporations%20accountable%20for%20consumer%20junk%20fees%2C%20predatory%20debt%20collection%2C%20worker%20mistreatment%2C%20profiteering%20off%20mom-and-pop%20shops%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20seeing%20national%20law%20firms%20put%20out%20warnings%20that%20big%2C%20blue-chip%20companies%20need%20to%20be%20paying%20attention%20to%20New%20York%20City%20law%20because%20we%20have%20an%20enforcement%20agency%20like%20DCWP%20ready%20to%20enforce%20these%20laws%20aggressively%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Levine%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3ed99ee218c3b62535df03%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225805%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEven%20on%20a%20day%20off%2C%20Levine%20said%20he%20spends%20a%20few%20hours%20working.%20Maybe%20he'll%20attend%20a%20friend's%20birthday%20party%20or%20catch%20up%20on%20laundry%2C%20too.%3Cp%3ECorrie%20Aune%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20found%20examples%20of%20this%20at%20Big%20Law%20firms%20like%20Gibson%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDunn%20and%20Skadden%2C%20Arps%2C%20Slate%2C%20Meagher%20%26amp%3B%20Flom.%20Joe%20Doherty%20%E2%80%94%20who%20is%20chief%20legal%20officer%20for%20the%20Self%20Storage%20Association%2C%20a%20trade%20group%20that%20supports%20companies%20like%20Extra%20Space%20and%20U-Haul%20%E2%80%94%20said%20he's%20advising%20the%20companies%20he%20works%20with%20to%20closely%20read%20local%20regulations%20and%20licensing%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20sued%20Extra%20Space%20in%20February%2C%20alleging%20predatory%20pricing%20practices%20that%20harm%20consumers%2C%20and%20the%20case%20was%20settled%20for%20%241.7%20million%20on%20July%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20company%20spokesperson%20said%20they%20%26quot%3Bdisagree%20with%20the%20claims%20being%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20they%20can't%20comment%20on%20the%20legal%20process.%20Doherty%20told%20me%20that%20DCWP's%20online%20subscription%20regulations%20could%20leave%20storage%20providers%20in%20a%20position%20where%20customers%20can%20abandon%20a%20unit%20without%C2%A0removing%20their%20property.%20%26quot%3BIf%20(the%20department)%20were%20more%20open%20to%20speaking%20to%20our%20industry%2C%20they'd%20have%20an%20opportunity%20to%20understand%20why%20these%20don't%20work%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Levine's%20view%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20big-name%20companies%20that%20should%20be%20paying%20attention.%20The%20department%20recently%20announced%20an%20action%20against%20a%20small%20Bronx%20auto%20dealer%20for%20%26quot%3Bovercharging%26quot%3B%20customers%20with%20%26quot%3Bbait-and-switch%26quot%3B%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELigia%20Guallpa%20described%20her%20work%20with%20Levine%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpartnership.%26quot%3B%20She's%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Workers'%20Justice%20Project%2C%20an%20organization%20that%20represents%20cleaners%2C%20construction%20workers%2C%20and%20delivery%20drivers%20in%20NYC.%20She%20mentioned%20the%20%241%20million%20government-funded%20Deliverista%20Hub%2C%20a%20new%20space%20for%20delivery%20workers%20to%20shelter%20from%20the%20weather%20and%20access%20support%20services%2C%20as%20an%20example%20of%20how%20the%20administration%20is%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20to%20moving%20resources%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%20to%20deliver%20on%20every%20promise%20for%20workers.%26quot%3B%20The%20commissioner%20visited%20the%20lower%20Manhattan%20hub%20in%20mid-June%20to%20speak%20with%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227793%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Levine%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3ed7aa360acd489560c22a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225195%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELevine%20emphasized%20that%20he's%20a%20worker%20and%20consumer%20himself.%20His%20first%20job%20was%20bagging%20food%20at%20a%20grocery%20store.%3Cp%3ECorrie%20Aune%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Levine%20is%20preparing%20for%20the%20future.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20scale%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20His%20goal%20%26quot%3Bisn't%20just%20to%20address%20the%20ways%20people%20are%20being%20nickel-and-dimed%20today%2C%20it's%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20the%20emerging%20challenges%20are%20and%20get%20ahead%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20starts%20with%20big%20goals%3A%20Going%20after%20companies%20that%20use%20AI%20and%20personal%20data%20surveillance%20to%20set%20gig%20worker%20wages%20or%20grocery%20prices.%20And%20the%20little%20things%3A%20like%20reporting%20convenience%20giant%20CVS%20for%20distributing%20an%20expired%20coupon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20Levine%20is%20a%20consumer%20with%20gripes%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOh%20my%20God%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20throwing%20his%20head%20back%20with%20a%20laugh.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20so%20many.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmamdani-work-consumer-czar-ripoffs-business-practices-sam-levine-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783846801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3ed9d3e218c3b62535df1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmamdani-work-consumer-czar-ripoffs-business-practices-sam-levine-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sam%20Levine%20runs%20the%20NYC%20Department%20of%20Consumer%20and%20Worker%20Protection.%20He%20told%20BI%20about%20his%20consumer%20gripes%20and%20Taco%20Bell%20celebration%20with%20Mamdani.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22allisonkelly%40businessinsider.com%20(Allie%20Kelly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22a