e-bet-to-transform-up-delhi-ncr-11751976%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-tunnel-one-highway-rs-14-115-crore-bet-to-transform-up-delhi-ncr-11751976%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20UK%20politician%20Ann%20Widdecombe%20murder%20probe%3A%20Police%20arrest%2028-year-old%20man%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783845943000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132343030%2Cimgsize-1306578.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fformer-uk-politician-ann-widdecombe-murder-probe-police-arrest-28-year-old-man%2Farticleshow%2F132342965.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F132342965.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fformer-uk-politician-ann-widdecombe-murder-probe-police-arrest-28-year-old-man%2Farticleshow%2F132342965.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fformer-uk-politician-ann-widdecombe-murder-probe-police-arrest-28-year-old-man%2Famp_articleshow%2F132342965.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fformer-uk-politician-ann-widdecombe-murder-probe-police-arrest-28-year-old-man%2Famp_articleshow%2F132342965.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20traded%20San%20Francisco's%20startup%20scene%20for%20a%20quieter%20life%20in%20Buenos%20Aires.%20It's%20helped%20me%20build%20a%20family.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sunflower%20founder%20Koby%20Conrad%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5002a1d3b3e4576519733d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKoby%20Conrad%20said%20that%20San%20Francisco%20was%20%26quot%3Breally%20good%20for%20early-career%20humans.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECaroline%20Tran%2FSelina%20Pan%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKoby%20Conrad%20moved%20from%20San%20Francisco%20to%20Buenos%20Aires%20to%20build%20a%20family.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20the%20food%2C%20I%20love%20the%20culture%2C%20and%20I%20love%20the%20fact%20that%20my%20rent%20is%2010x%20cheaper%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EConrad%20founded%20Sunflower%2C%20an%20AI%20sobriety%20companion.%20He%20said%20that%20he's%20more%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsober-startup-founders-younger-drinking-less-alcohol-2025-8%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elocked%20in%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%20Buenos%20Aires.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Koby%20Conrad%2C%20the%2032-year-old%20founder%20of%20Sunflower%2C%20an%20AI%20companion%20for%20sobriety.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20originally%20from%20Boise%2C%20Idaho%2C%20and%20didn't%20even%20realize%20tech%20was%20a%20thing.%20My%20little%20brother%20convinced%20me%20to%20move%20to%20San%20Francisco%20when%20I%20was%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20had%20this%202%2C000-square-foot%20house%2C%20and%20my%20mortgage%20was%20like%20%24900%20a%20month.%20In%20San%20Francisco%2C%20I%20moved%20in%20with%20nine%20roommates%2C%20where%20I%20was%20paying%20%241%2C600%20for%20this%20tiny%20little%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20little%20brother%20applied%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-y-combinator-founders-are-pitching-the-ai-boom-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EY%20Combinator%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20I%20had%20never%20heard%20of%2C%20and%20he%20put%20me%20down%20as%20his%20cofounder.%20That's%20how%20I%20got%20into%20YC%3A%20Quit%20your%20job%2C%20move%20to%20SF%2C%20and%20six%20weeks%20later%20you%20get%20in.%20Classic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20San%20Francisco.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20most%20gorgeous%20cities%20on%20the%20face%20of%20the%20planet.%20You're%20surrounded%20by%20nature%2C%20really%20smart%20people%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-eat-in-san-francisco-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20food%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20in%20SF%20is%20like%20peaking%20over%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20universe%20and%20seeing%20what's%20coming%20next.%20That's%20my%20biggest%20fear%20about%20not%20being%20in%20San%20Francisco%3A%20the%20world's%20going%20to%20move%2C%20and%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flip%20side%20of%20that%20is%2C%20if%20you're%20in%20SF%2C%20you're%20around%20a%20specific%20type%20of%20person%20all%20the%20time.%20Highly%20technical%20humans%20who%20work%20at%20tech%20companies%20is%2090%25%20of%20the%20circle.%20I%20think%20it's%20really%20good%20for%20early-career%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22afd14895-03c5-4659-9508-0ef5b9604a06%5C%22%3EI'm%20loving%20Buenos%20Aires%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20locked%20in%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELeaving%20a%20city%20is%20like%20breaking%20up%20with%20an%20ex.%20You%20want%20someone%20better%20after%2C%20and%20you%20never%20want%20to%20downgrade.%20I%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20I%20find%20a%20city%20that%20is%20better%20than%20SF%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20two%20options%3A%20New%20York%20or%20Buenos%20Aires.%20I%20spent%20a%20bunch%20of%20time%20in%20both%2C%20but%20ultimately%20I%20decided%20that%20I%20really%20like%20Buenos%20Aires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20does%20a%20really%20good%20job%20of%20romanticizing%20Europe%20and%20Asia%2C%20but%20we%20never%20think%20of%20Latin%20America.%20At%20my%20old%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvcs-most-promising-startups-healthtech-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERupa%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20would%20do%20our%20off-sites%20in%20Mexico%20and%20Costa%20Rica.%20We%20had%20a%20bunch%20of%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20brain%20really%20likes%20learning%20things.%20Learning%20a%20second%20language%20and%20being%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20everything%20is%20new%20is%20super%20stimulating%20for%20my%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20the%20food%2C%20I%20love%20the%20culture%2C%20and%20I%20love%20the%20fact%20that%20my%20rent%20is%2010x%20cheaper.%20In%20SF%2C%20if%20I'm%20making%20%24300%2C000%2C%20I'm%20still%20stressed%20about%20money.%20Here%2C%20you%20can%20make%20%24100%2C000%20and%20think%3A%20%26quot%3BCool%2C%20I'm%20set%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20that%20some%20parts%20of%20Latin%20America%20are%20dangerous.%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedellin-colombia-is-south-americas-best-destination-2016-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20Medell%C3%ADn%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20bit%20and%20almost%20got%20kidnapped%20while%20walking%20up%20to%20the%20airplane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArgentina%20is%20one%20of%20the%20safest%20places%20in%20Latin%20America.%20Buenos%20Aires%20is%20the%20safest%20city%20across%20multiple%20dimensions.%20There%20are%20people%20walking%20their%20kids%20in%20strollers.%20You%20don't%20have%20the%20earthquake%20fear.%20The%20cops%20are%20amazing%20here%20and%20won't%20shake%20you%20down.%20Argentines%20are%20amazingly%20friendly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20coming%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20country%20every%20three%20months.%20Not%20being%20in%20SF%20means%20I%20travel%20to%20it%20frequently.%20I%20am%20applying%20for%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-nomad-visas-countries%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enomad%20visa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20super%20happy%20here.%20I'm%20about%20to%20have%20a%20baby%2C%20my%20girlfriend%20is%20here%2C%20and%20we're%20about%20to%20get%20a%20gorgeous%20office%20space.%20Technical%20talent%20will%20be%20in%20SF%20and%20New%20York%2C%20but%20the%20go-to-market%20team%20will%20be%20in%20Buenos%20Aires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20super%20locked%20in%20here.%20When%20I%20go%20to%20San%20Francisco%2C%20it's%20like%3A%20here's%20a%20poker%20game%2C%20here's%20a%20founder%20dinner%20party%2C%20here's%20an%20investor%20event%20you%20need%20to%20go%20to.%20When%20I'm%20in%20Argentina%2C%20I%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20but%20work%2024%2F7.%20I%20have%20a%20full-time%20house%20manager%20who%20feeds%20me%20and%20does%20my%20laundry%20to%20make%20sure%20there's%20nothing%20I%20have%20to%20do%20besides%20work.%20It's%20like%20living%20under%20a%20rock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20reason%20I%20moved%2010%2C000%20kilometers%20away.%20I'm%20not%20a%20very%20social%20creature.%20I'm%20a%20nerd%20who%20used%20to%20play%20a%20bunch%20of%20%26quot%3BRuneScape%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-world-of-warcraft-is-so-popular-2016-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20of%20Warcraft%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20For%20me%2C%20tech%20startups%20are%20an%20extension%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2229a1bff3-4b43-453c-a35b-197b94921226%5C%22%3EIt's%20difficult%20to%20have%20kids%20in%20San%20Francisco%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20really%20hard%20to%20be%20able%20to%20have%20a%20house%20or%20apartment%20that's%20big%20enough%20to%20have%20a%20baby%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20You%20either%20need%20a%20spouse%20that%20doesn't%20work%C2%A0or%20you%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20hire%20childcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20founder%2C%20I%20have%20employees%20who%20are%20pregnant%2C%20and%20they're%20going%20to%20have%20three%20months%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-companies-maternity-parental-leave-policies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ematernity%20leave%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20can't%20have%20three%20months%20of%20leave.%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20out%20of%20the%20office%20for%20two%20weeks%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20six%20years%3B%20that's%20my%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20my%20job%20and%20have%20kids%2C%20I%20have%20to%20be%20able%20to%20sleep%20and%20take%20care%20of%20them%20during%20the%20day.%20That's%20on%20top%20of%20having%20an%20extra%20bedroom.%20It%20would%20cost%20me%20half%20a%20million%20dollars%20to%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20that%20lifestyle%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20most%20ambitious%20founders%20I've%20met%20haven't%20been%20in%20SF.%20Our%20ambitions%20should%20include%20kids%20and%20family.%20That's%20the%20reason%20most%20people%20want%20to%20have%20a%20%2410%20million%20outcome.%20I%20want%20to%20build%20massive%20things%2C%20have%20kids%2C%20and%20leave%20it%20all%20to%20them.%20That%20is%20a%20major%20drive%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20give%20up%20so%20much%20by%20being%20in%20those%20cities.%20The%20opportunity%20cost%20is%20crazy.%20If%20you're%20a%20founder%20and%20want%20to%20have%20a%20family%2C%20you%20basically%20have%20to%20be%20already%20exited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-from-san-francisco-buenos-aires-argentina-family-having-kids-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783845901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5002a1d3b3e4576519733d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-from-san-francisco-buenos-aires-argentina-family-having-kids-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sunflower%20cofounder%20Koby%20Conrad%20moved%20from%20San%20Francisco%20to%20Buenos%20Aires.%20Its%20helped%20him%20%26quot%3Block%20in%26quot%3